ething hit the back of his neck an\"}]","[{\"text\":\"agonizingly painful blow. It was as though a red-hot wire had been jabbed\"},{\"text\":\"into him. He spun round just in time to see Mrs Parsons dragging her son\"},{\"text\":\"back into the doorway while the boy pocketed a catapult.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"door closed on him. But what most\"},{\"text\":\"struck Winston was the look of helpless fright on the woman's greyish face.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Back in the flat he stepped quickly past the telescreen and sat down at the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"telescreen had\"},{\"text\":\"stopped. Instead, a clipped military voice was reading out, with a sort of\"},{\"text\":\"brutal relish, a description of the armaments of the new Floating Fortress\"},{\"text\":\"which had just been anchored between Iceland and the Faroe Islands.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"With those children, he thought, that wretched woman must lead a life of\"},{\"text\":\"terror. Another year, two years, and they would be watching her night\"},{\"text\":\"and day for symptoms of unorthodoxy. Nearly all children nowadays were\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that by means of such organizations as\"},{\"text\":\"the Spies they were systematically turned into ungovernable little savages,\"},{\"text\":\"and yet this produced in them no tendency whatever to rebel against the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the Party and\"},{\"text\":\"everything connected with it. The songs, the processions, the banners, the\"},{\"text\":\"hiking, the drilling with dummy rifles, the yelling of slogans, the worship\"},{\"text\":\"of Big Brother--it was all a sort of glorious game to them. All their\"}]","[{\"text\":\"turned outwards, against the enemies of the State, against\"},{\"text\":\"foreigners, traitors, saboteurs, thought-criminals. It was almost normal\"},{\"text\":\"for people over thirty to be frightened of their own children. And with\"}]","[{\"text\":\"in which 'The Times' did not carry\"},{\"text\":\"a paragraph 