ly survive?\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The telescreen struck fourteen. He must leave in ten minutes. He had to be\"},{\"text\":\"back at work by fourteen-thirty.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"seemed to have put new heart into him.\"},{\"text\":\"He was a lonely ghost uttering a truth that nobody would ever hear. But so\"},{\"text\":\"long as he uttered it, in some obscure way the continuity was not broken.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that you carried on\"},{\"text\":\"the human heritage. He went back to the table, dipped his pen, and wrote:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"free, when men\"},{\"text\":\"are different from one another and do not live alone--to a time when truth\"},{\"text\":\"exists and what is done cannot be undone:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"from the age of\"},{\"text\":\"Big Brother, from the age of doublethink--greetings!\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He was already dead, he reflected. It seemed to him that it was only now,\"},{\"text\":\"when he had begun to be able to formulate his thoughts, that he had taken\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the decisive step. The consequences of every act are included in the act\"},{\"text\":\"itself. He wrote:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Thoughtcrime does not entail death: thoughtcrime IS death.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Now he had recognized himself as a dead man it became important to stay\"},{\"text\":\"alive as long as possible. Two fingers of his right hand were inkstained.\"},{\"text\":\"It was exactly the kind of detail that might betray you. Some nosing zealot\"}]","[{\"text\":\"someone like the little sandy-haired\"},{\"text\":\"woman or the dark-haired girl from the Fiction Department) might start\"},{\"text\":\"wondering why he had been writing during the lunch interval, why he had\"},{\"text\":\"used an old-fashioned pen, WHAT he ha