te for thirty seconds. It was nought seven fifteen, getting-up\"}]","[{\"text\":\"wrenched his body out of bed--naked, for\"},{\"text\":\"a member of the Outer Party received only 3,000 clothing coupons annually,\"},{\"text\":\"and a suit of pyjamas was 600--and seized a dingy singlet and a pair of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Jerks would begin in\"},{\"text\":\"three minutes. The next moment he was doubled up by a violent coughing fit\"},{\"text\":\"which nearly always attacked him soon after waking up. It emptied his lungs\"},{\"text\":\"so completely that he could only begin breathing again by lying on his back\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and taking a series of deep gasps. His veins had swelled with the effort of\"},{\"text\":\"the cough, and the varicose ulcer had started itching.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Thirty to forty group!' yapped a piercing female voice. 'Thirty to forty\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Thirties to forties!'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston sprang to attention in front of the telescreen, upon which the\"},{\"text\":\"image of a youngish woman, scrawny but muscular, dressed in tunic and\"},{\"text\":\"gym-shoes, had already appeared.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Arms bending and stretching!' she rapped out. 'Take your time by me. ONE,\"},{\"text\":\"two, three, four! ONE, two, three, four! Come on, comrades, put a bit of\"},{\"text\":\"life into it! ONE, two, three four! ONE two, three, four!...'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"coughing fit had not quite driven out of Winston's mind the\"},{\"text\":\"impression made by his dream, and the rhythmic movements of the exercise\"},{\"text\":\"restored it somewhat. As he mechanically shot his arms back and forth,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"enjoyment which was considered proper\"},{\"text\":\"during the Physical Jerks, he was struggling to think his way backward into\"},{\"text\":\"the dim period of his early childhood. It was extraordinarily difficult.\"},{\"text\":\"Beyond the late fifties everything faded. When 