trols the future: who controls the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the past, though of its nature\"},{\"text\":\"alterable, never had been altered. Whatever was true now was true from\"},{\"text\":\"everlasting to everlasting. It was quite simple. All that was needed was\"},{\"text\":\"an unending series of victories over your own memory. 'Reality control',\"}]","[{\"text\":\"they called it: in Newspeak, 'doublethink'.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Stand easy!' barked the instructress, a little more genially.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston sank his arms to his sides and slowly refilled his lungs with air.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"into the labyrinthine world of doublethink. To know\"},{\"text\":\"and not to know, to be conscious of complete truthfulness while telling\"},{\"text\":\"carefully constructed lies, to hold simultaneously two opinions which\"}]","[{\"text\":\"believing in both of\"},{\"text\":\"them, to use logic against logic, to repudiate morality while laying claim\"},{\"text\":\"to it, to believe that democracy was impossible and that the Party was the\"},{\"text\":\"guardian of democracy, to forget whatever it was necessary to forget, then\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to draw it back into memory again at the moment when it was needed, and\"},{\"text\":\"then promptly to forget it again: and above all, to apply the same process\"},{\"text\":\"to the process itself. That was the ultimate subtlety: consciously to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"once again, to become unconscious of\"},{\"text\":\"the act of hypnosis you had just performed. Even to understand the word\"},{\"text\":\"'doublethink' involved the use of doublethink.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The instructress had called them to attention again. 'And now let's see\"}]","[{\"text\":\"which of us can touch our toes!' she said enthusiastically. 'Right over\"},{\"text\":\"from the hips, please, comrades. ONE-two! ONE-two!...'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston loathed this exercise, which sent shooting pains all the way from\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ended by bringing on another coughing\"},{\"text\":\"fit. The half-pleasant quality went out of his meditations. The past, he\"},{\"text\":\"reflected, had not merely been altered, it had been actually destroyed. For\"},{\"text\":\"how could you establish even the most obvious fact when there existed no\"}]","[{\"text\":\"record outside your own memory? He tried to remember in what year he had\"},{\"text\":\"first heard mention of Big Brother. He thought it must have been at some\"},{\"text\":\"time in the sixties, but it was impossible to be certain. In the Party\"}]","[{\"text\":\"figured as the leader and guardian of the\"},{\"text\":\"Revolution since its very earliest days. His exploits had been gradually\"},{\"text\":\"pushed backwards in time until already they extended into the fabulous\"}]","[{\"text\":\"capitalists in their\"},{\"text\":\"strange cylindrical hats still rode through the streets of London in great\"},{\"text\":\"gleaming motor-cars or horse carriages with glass sides. There was no\"},{\"text\":\"knowing how much of this legend was true and how much invented. Winston\"}]","[{\"text\":\"could not even remember at what date the Party itself had come into\"},{\"text\":\"existence. He did not believe he had ever heard the word Ingsoc before\"},{\"text\":\"1960, but it was possible that in its Oldspeak form--'English Socialism',\"}]","[{\"text\":\"earlier. Everything melted into mist.\"},{\"text\":\"Sometimes, indeed, you could put your finger on a definite lie. It was not\"},{\"text\":\"true, for example, as was claimed in the Party history books, that the\"},{\"text\":\"Party had invented aeroplanes. He remembered aeroplanes since his earliest\"}]","[{\"text\":\"childhood. But you could prove nothing. There was never any evidence. Just\"},{\"text\":\"once in his whole life he had held in his hands unmistakable documentary\"},{\"text\":\"proof of the falsification of an historical fact. And on that occasion----\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the shrewish voice from the telescreen. '6079 Smith W.!\"},{\"text\":\"Yes, YOU! Bend lower, please! You can do better than that. You're not\"},{\"text\":\"trying. Lower, please! THAT'S better, comrade. Now stand at ease, the\"},{\"text\":\"whole squad, and watch me.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"A sudden hot sweat had broken out all over Winston's body. His face\"},{\"text\":\"remained completely inscrutable. Never show dismay! Never show resentment!\"},{\"text\":\"A single flicker of the eyes could give you away. He stood watching while\"}]","[{\"text\":\"above her head and--one could not say\"},{\"text\":\"gracefully, but with remarkable neatness and efficiency--bent over and\"},{\"text\":\"tucked the first joint of her fingers under her toes.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'THERE, comrades! THAT'S how I want to see you doing it. Watch me again.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"I'm thirty-nine and I've had four children. Now look.' She bent over again.\"},{\"text\":\"'You see MY knees aren't bent. You can all do it if you want to,' she added\"},{\"text\":\"as she straightened herself up. 'Anyone under forty-five is perfectly\"}]","[{\"text\":\"don't all have the privilege of fighting\"},{\"text\":\"in the front line, but at least we can all keep fit. Remember our boys on\"},{\"text\":\"the Malabar front! And the sailors in the Floating Fortresses! Just think\"}]","[{\"text\":\"better, comrade,\"},{\"text\":\"that's MUCH better,' she added encouragingly as Winston, with a violent\"},{\"text\":\"lunge, succeeded in touching his toes with knees unbent, for the first\"},{\"text\":\"time in several years.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Chapter 4\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"With the deep, unconscious sigh which not even the nearness of the\"},{\"text\":\"telescreen could prevent him from uttering when his day's work started,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"him, blew the dust from its\"},{\"text\":\"mouthpiece, and put on his spectacles. Then he unrolled and clipped\"},{\"text\":\"together four small cylinders of paper which had already flopped out of\"},{\"text\":\"the pneumatic tube on the right-hand side of his desk.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"In the walls of the cubicle there were three orifices. To the right of the\"},{\"text\":\"speakwrite, a small pneumatic tube for written messages, to the left, a\"},{\"text\":\"larger one for newspapers; and in the side wall, within easy reach of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"protected by a wire grating. This last\"},{\"text\":\"was for the disposal of waste paper. Similar slits existed in thousands or\"},{\"text\":\"tens of thousands throughout the building, not only in every room but at\"}]","[{\"text\":\"were nicknamed\"},{\"text\":\"memory holes. When one knew that any document was due for destruction, or\"},{\"text\":\"even when one saw a scrap of waste paper lying about, it was an automatic\"},{\"text\":\"action to lift the flap of the nearest memory hole and drop it in,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"be whirled away on a current of warm air to the enormous\"},{\"text\":\"furnaces which were hidden somewhere in the recesses of the building.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston examined the four slips of paper which he had unrolled. Each\"}]","[{\"text\":\"two lines, in the abbreviated\"},{\"text\":\"jargon--not actually Newspeak, but consisting\"},{\"text\":\"largely of Newspeak words--which was used in the Ministry for internal\"},{\"text\":\"purposes. They ran:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"speech malreported africa rectify\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"times 19.12.83 forecasts 3 yp 4th quarter 83 misprints verify current issue\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"times 14.2.84 miniplenty malquoted chocolate rectify\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"doubleplusungood refs unpersons rewrite\"},{\"text\":\"fullwise upsub antefiling\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"With a faint feeling of satisfaction Winston laid the fourth message aside.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"be dealt with last.\"},{\"text\":\"The other three were routine matters, though the second one would probably\"},{\"text\":\"mean some tedious wading through lists of figures.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston dialled 'back numbers' on the telescreen and called for the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"appropriate issues of 'The Times', which slid out of the pneumatic tube\"},{\"text\":\"after only a few minutes' delay. The messages he had received referred to\"},{\"text\":\"articles or news items which for one reason or another it was thought\"}]","[{\"text\":\"official phrase had it, to rectify. For\"},{\"text\":\"example, it appeared from 'The Times' of the seventeenth of March that Big\"},{\"text\":\"Brother, in his speech of the previous day, had predicted that the South\"}]","[{\"text\":\"offensive would shortly\"},{\"text\":\"be launched in North Africa. As it happened, the Eurasian Higher Command\"},{\"text\":\"had launched its offensive in South India and left North Africa alone. It\"},{\"text\":\"was therefore necessary to rewrite a paragraph of Big Brother's speech, in\"}]","[{\"text\":\"such a way as to make him predict the thing that had actually happened. Or\"},{\"text\":\"again, 'The Times' of the nineteenth of December had published the official\"},{\"text\":\"forecasts of the output of various classes of consumption goods in the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"also the sixth quarter of the Ninth\"},{\"text\":\"Three-Year Plan. Today's issue contained a statement of the actual output,\"},{\"text\":\"from which it appeared that the forecasts were in every instance grossly\"},{\"text\":\"wrong. Winston's job was to rectify the original figures by making them\"}]","[{\"text\":\"agree with the later ones. As for the third message, it referred to a very\"},{\"text\":\"simple error which could be set right in a couple of minutes. As short\"},{\"text\":\"a time ago as February, the Ministry of Plenty had issued a promise\"}]","[{\"text\":\"official words) that there would be\"},{\"text\":\"no reduction of the chocolate ration during 1984. Actually, as Winston\"},{\"text\":\"was aware, the chocolate ration was to be reduced from thirty grammes\"},{\"text\":\"to twenty at the end of the present week. All that was needed was to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"substitute for the original promise a warning that it would probably be\"},{\"text\":\"necessary to reduce the ration at some time in April.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"As soon as Winston had dealt with each of the messages, he clipped his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"appropriate copy of 'The Times' and pushed\"},{\"text\":\"them into the pneumatic tube. Then, with a movement which was as nearly as\"},{\"text\":\"possible unconscious, he crumpled up the original message and any notes\"}]","[{\"text\":\"memory hole to be\"},{\"text\":\"devoured by the flames.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"What happened in the unseen labyrinth to which the pneumatic tubes led, he\"},{\"text\":\"did not know in detail, but he did know in general terms. As soon as all\"}]","[{\"text\":\"necessary in any particular number\"},{\"text\":\"of 'The Times' had been assembled and collated, that number would be\"},{\"text\":\"reprinted, the original copy destroyed, and the corrected copy placed on\"},{\"text\":\"the files in its stead. This process of continuous alteration was applied\"}]","[{\"text\":\"not only to newspapers, but to books, periodicals, pamphlets, posters,\"},{\"text\":\"leaflets, films, sound-tracks, cartoons, photographs--to every kind of\"},{\"text\":\"literature or documentation which might conceivably hold any political or\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and almost minute by minute the past\"},{\"text\":\"was brought up to date. In this way every prediction made by the Party\"},{\"text\":\"could be shown by documentary evidence to have been correct, nor was any\"},{\"text\":\"item of news, or any expression of opinion, which conflicted with the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"needs of the moment, ever allowed to remain on record. All history was\"},{\"text\":\"a palimpsest, scraped clean and reinscribed exactly as often as was\"},{\"text\":\"necessary. In no case would it have been possible, once the deed was done,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"taken place. The largest section of\"},{\"text\":\"the Records Department, far larger than the one on which Winston worked,\"},{\"text\":\"consisted simply of persons whose duty it was to track down and collect all\"},{\"text\":\"copies of books, newspapers, and other documents which had been superseded\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and were due for destruction. A number of 'The Times' which might, because\"},{\"text\":\"of changes in political alignment, or mistaken prophecies uttered by Big\"},{\"text\":\"Brother, have been rewritten a dozen times still stood on the files bearing\"}]","[{\"text\":\"existed to contradict it. Books, also,\"},{\"text\":\"were recalled and rewritten again and again, and were invariably reissued\"},{\"text\":\"without any admission that any alteration had been made. Even the written\"}]","[{\"text\":\"invariably got rid of\"},{\"text\":\"as soon as he had dealt with them, never stated or implied that an act of\"},{\"text\":\"forgery was to be committed: always the reference was to slips, errors,\"},{\"text\":\"misprints, or misquotations which it was necessary to put right in the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"interests of accuracy.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"But actually, he thought as he re-adjusted the Ministry of Plenty's\"},{\"text\":\"figures, it was not even forgery. It was merely the substitution of one\"}]","[{\"text\":\"you were dealing\"},{\"text\":\"with had no connexion with anything in the real world, not even the kind of\"},{\"text\":\"connexion that is contained in a direct lie. Statistics were just as much\"},{\"text\":\"a fantasy in their original version as in their rectified version. A great\"}]","[{\"text\":\"you were expected to make them up out of your head. For\"},{\"text\":\"example, the Ministry of Plenty's forecast had estimated the output of\"},{\"text\":\"boots for the quarter at 145 million pairs. The actual output was given as\"}]","[{\"text\":\"forecast, marked\"},{\"text\":\"the figure down to fifty-seven millions, so as to allow for the usual claim\"},{\"text\":\"that the quota had been overfulfilled. In any case, sixty-two millions was\"},{\"text\":\"no nearer the truth than fifty-seven millions, or than 145 millions. Very\"}]","[{\"text\":\"had been produced at all. Likelier still, nobody knew\"},{\"text\":\"how many had been produced, much less cared. All one knew was that every\"},{\"text\":\"quarter astronomical numbers of boots were produced on paper, while perhaps\"}]","[{\"text\":\"was with every\"},{\"text\":\"class of recorded fact, great or small. Everything faded away into a\"},{\"text\":\"shadow-world in which, finally, even the date of the year had become\"},{\"text\":\"uncertain.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"cubicle on the other\"},{\"text\":\"side a small, precise-looking, dark-chinned man named Tillotson was working\"},{\"text\":\"steadily away, with a folded newspaper on his knee and his mouth very close\"},{\"text\":\"to the mouthpiece of the speakwrite. He had the air of trying to keep what\"}]","[{\"text\":\"he was saying a secret between himself and the telescreen. He looked up,\"},{\"text\":\"and his spectacles darted a hostile flash in Winston's direction.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston hardly knew Tillotson, and had no idea what work he was employed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Records Department did not readily talk about their jobs.\"},{\"text\":\"In the long, windowless hall, with its double row of cubicles and its\"},{\"text\":\"endless rustle of papers and hum of voices murmuring into speakwrites,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston did not even know by name,\"},{\"text\":\"though he daily saw them hurrying to and fro in the corridors or\"},{\"text\":\"gesticulating in the Two Minutes Hate. He knew that in the cubicle next\"},{\"text\":\"to him the little woman with sandy hair toiled day in day out, simply at\"}]","[{\"text\":\"tracking down and deleting from the Press the names of people who had been\"},{\"text\":\"vaporized and were therefore considered never to have existed. There was a\"},{\"text\":\"certain fitness in this, since her own husband had been vaporized a couple\"}]","[{\"text\":\"away a mild, ineffectual, dreamy\"},{\"text\":\"creature named Ampleforth, with very hairy ears and a surprising talent\"},{\"text\":\"for juggling with rhymes and metres, was engaged in producing garbled\"},{\"text\":\"versions--definitive texts, they were called--of poems which had become\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ideologically offensive, but which for one reason or another were to be\"},{\"text\":\"retained in the anthologies. And this hall, with its fifty workers or\"},{\"text\":\"thereabouts, was only one sub-section, a single cell, as it were, in the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Department. Beyond, above, below, were other\"},{\"text\":\"swarms of workers engaged in an unimaginable multitude of jobs. There were\"},{\"text\":\"the huge printing-shops with their sub-editors, their typography experts,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"photographs. There\"},{\"text\":\"was the tele-programmes section with its engineers, its producers, and its\"},{\"text\":\"teams of actors specially chosen for their skill in imitating voices. There\"},{\"text\":\"were the armies of reference clerks whose job was simply to draw up lists\"}]","[{\"text\":\"periodicals which were due for recall. There were the vast\"},{\"text\":\"repositories where the corrected documents were stored, and the hidden\"},{\"text\":\"furnaces where the original copies were destroyed. And somewhere or other,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"directing brains who co-ordinated the whole\"},{\"text\":\"effort and laid down the lines of policy which made it necessary that this\"},{\"text\":\"fragment of the past should be preserved, that one falsified, and the other\"},{\"text\":\"rubbed out of existence.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"And the Records Department, after all, was itself only a single branch of\"},{\"text\":\"the Ministry of Truth, whose primary job was not to reconstruct the past\"},{\"text\":\"but to supply the citizens of Oceania with newspapers, films, textbooks,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"novels--with every conceivable kind of\"},{\"text\":\"information, instruction, or entertainment, from a statue to a slogan,\"},{\"text\":\"from a lyric poem to a biological treatise, and from a child's\"}]","[{\"text\":\"had not only to\"},{\"text\":\"supply the multifarious needs of the party, but also to repeat the whole\"},{\"text\":\"operation at a lower level for the benefit of the proletariat. There\"},{\"text\":\"was a whole chain of separate departments dealing with proletarian\"}]","[{\"text\":\"drama, and entertainment generally. Here were produced\"},{\"text\":\"rubbishy newspapers containing almost nothing except sport, crime and\"},{\"text\":\"astrology, sensational five-cent novelettes, films oozing with sex, and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"mechanical means on a\"},{\"text\":\"special kind of kaleidoscope known as a versificator. There was even\"},{\"text\":\"a whole sub-section--Pornosec, it was called in Newspeak--engaged in\"},{\"text\":\"producing the lowest kind of pornography, which was sent out in sealed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"packets and which no Party member, other than those who worked on it,\"},{\"text\":\"was permitted to look at.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Three messages had slid out of the pneumatic tube while Winston was\"}]","[{\"text\":\"disposed of them before\"},{\"text\":\"the Two Minutes Hate interrupted him. When the Hate was over he returned\"},{\"text\":\"to his cubicle, took the Newspeak dictionary from the shelf, pushed the\"},{\"text\":\"speakwrite to one side, cleaned his spectacles, and settled down to his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"main job of the morning.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston's greatest pleasure in life was in his work. Most of it was a\"},{\"text\":\"tedious routine, but included in it there were also jobs so difficult and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"depths of a\"},{\"text\":\"mathematical problem--delicate pieces of forgery in which you had nothing\"},{\"text\":\"to guide you except your knowledge of the principles of Ingsoc and your\"},{\"text\":\"estimate of what the Party wanted you to say. Winston was good at this kind\"}]","[{\"text\":\"occasion he had even been entrusted with the rectification of\"},{\"text\":\"'The Times' leading articles, which were written entirely in Newspeak.\"},{\"text\":\"He unrolled the message that he had set aside earlier. It ran:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"times 3.12.83 reporting bb dayorder doubleplusungood refs unpersons\"},{\"text\":\"rewrite fullwise upsub antefiling\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"In Oldspeak (or standard English) this might be rendered:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The reporting of Big Brother's Order for the Day in 'The Times' of December\"},{\"text\":\"3rd 1983 is extremely unsatisfactory and makes references to non-existent\"},{\"text\":\"persons. Rewrite it in full and submit your draft to higher authority\"},{\"text\":\"before filing.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston read through the offending article. Big Brother's Order for the\"},{\"text\":\"Day, it seemed, had been chiefly devoted to praising the work of an\"},{\"text\":\"organization known as FFCC, which supplied cigarettes and other comforts\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Fortresses. A certain Comrade Withers, a\"},{\"text\":\"prominent member of the Inner Party, had been singled out for special\"},{\"text\":\"mention and awarded a decoration, the Order of Conspicuous Merit, Second\"},{\"text\":\"Class.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"FFCC had suddenly been dissolved with no reasons given.\"},{\"text\":\"One could assume that Withers and his associates were now in disgrace, but\"},{\"text\":\"there had been no report of the matter in the Press or on the telescreen.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"political offenders to\"},{\"text\":\"be put on trial or even publicly denounced. The great purges involving\"},{\"text\":\"thousands of people, with public trials of traitors and thought-criminals\"},{\"text\":\"who made abject confession of their crimes and were afterwards executed,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"were special show-pieces not occurring oftener than once in a couple of\"},{\"text\":\"years. More commonly, people who had incurred the displeasure of the\"},{\"text\":\"Party simply disappeared and were never heard of again. One never had the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to them. In some cases they might\"},{\"text\":\"not even be dead. Perhaps thirty people personally known to Winston, not\"},{\"text\":\"counting his parents, had disappeared at one time or another.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the cubicle\"},{\"text\":\"across the way Comrade Tillotson was still crouching secretively over\"},{\"text\":\"his speakwrite. He raised his head for a moment: again the hostile\"},{\"text\":\"spectacle-flash. Winston wondered whether Comrade Tillotson was engaged\"}]","[{\"text\":\"himself. It was perfectly possible. So tricky a piece\"},{\"text\":\"of work would never be entrusted to a single person: on the other hand,\"},{\"text\":\"to turn it over to a committee would be to admit openly that an act of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"dozen people were\"},{\"text\":\"now working away on rival versions of what Big Brother had actually said.\"},{\"text\":\"And presently some master brain in the Inner Party would select this\"},{\"text\":\"version or that, would re-edit it and set in motion the complex processes\"}]","[{\"text\":\"cross-referencing that would be required, and then the chosen lie\"},{\"text\":\"would pass into the permanent records and become truth.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston did not know why Withers had been disgraced. Perhaps it was for\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Big Brother was merely getting rid of\"},{\"text\":\"a too-popular subordinate. Perhaps Withers or someone close to him had\"},{\"text\":\"been suspected of heretical tendencies. Or perhaps--what was likeliest of\"},{\"text\":\"all--the thing had simply happened because purges and vaporizations were a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"necessary part of the mechanics of government. The only real clue lay in\"},{\"text\":\"the words 'refs unpersons', which indicated that Withers was already dead.\"},{\"text\":\"You could not invariably assume this to be the case when people were\"}]","[{\"text\":\"released and allowed to remain at liberty\"},{\"text\":\"for as much as a year or two years before being executed. Very occasionally\"},{\"text\":\"some person whom you had believed dead long since would make a ghostly\"}]","[{\"text\":\"implicate hundreds of\"},{\"text\":\"others by his testimony before vanishing, this time for ever. Withers,\"},{\"text\":\"however, was already an UNPERSON. He did not exist: he had never existed.\"},{\"text\":\"Winston decided that it would not be enough simply to reverse the tendency\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of Big Brother's speech. It was better to make it deal with something\"},{\"text\":\"totally unconnected with its original subject.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He might turn the speech into the usual denunciation of traitors and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"little too obvious, while to invent a\"},{\"text\":\"victory at the front, or some triumph of over-production in the Ninth\"},{\"text\":\"Three-Year Plan, might complicate the records too much. What was needed\"},{\"text\":\"was a piece of pure fantasy. Suddenly there sprang into his mind, ready\"}]","[{\"text\":\"made as it were, the image of a certain Comrade Ogilvy, who had recently\"},{\"text\":\"died in battle, in heroic circumstances. There were occasions when Big\"},{\"text\":\"Brother devoted his Order for the Day to commemorating some humble,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and death he held up as an example\"},{\"text\":\"worthy to be followed. Today he should commemorate Comrade Ogilvy. It was\"},{\"text\":\"true that there was no such person as Comrade Ogilvy, but a few lines of\"},{\"text\":\"print and a couple of faked photographs would soon bring him into\"}]","[{\"text\":\"existence.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston thought for a moment, then pulled the speakwrite towards him and\"},{\"text\":\"began dictating in Big Brother's familiar style: a style at once military\"},{\"text\":\"and pedantic, and, because of a trick of asking questions and then\"}]","[{\"text\":\"promptly answering them ('What lessons do we learn from this fact,\"},{\"text\":\"comrades? The lesson--which is also one of the fundamental principles\"},{\"text\":\"of Ingsoc--that,' etc., etc.), easy to imitate.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"had refused all toys except a drum, a\"},{\"text\":\"sub-machine gun, and a model helicopter. At six--a year early, by a special\"},{\"text\":\"relaxation of the rules--he had joined the Spies, at nine he had been a\"},{\"text\":\"troop leader. At eleven he had denounced his uncle to the Thought Police\"}]","[{\"text\":\"after overhearing a conversation which appeared to him to have criminal\"},{\"text\":\"tendencies. At seventeen he had been a district organizer of the Junior\"},{\"text\":\"Anti-Sex League. At nineteen he had designed a hand-grenade which had\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and which, at its first trial, had\"},{\"text\":\"killed thirty-one Eurasian prisoners in one burst. At twenty-three he had\"},{\"text\":\"perished in action. Pursued by enemy jet planes while flying over the\"},{\"text\":\"Indian Ocean with important despatches, he had weighted his body with his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"machine gun and leapt out of the helicopter into deep water, despatches\"},{\"text\":\"and all--an end, said Big Brother, which it was impossible to contemplate\"},{\"text\":\"without feelings of envy. Big Brother added a few remarks on the purity\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Ogilvy's life. He was a total abstainer\"},{\"text\":\"and a nonsmoker, had no recreations except a daily hour in the gymnasium,\"},{\"text\":\"and had taken a vow of celibacy, believing marriage and the care of a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"devotion to duty.\"},{\"text\":\"He had no subjects of conversation except the principles of Ingsoc, and\"},{\"text\":\"no aim in life except the defeat of the Eurasian enemy and the hunting-down\"},{\"text\":\"of spies, saboteurs, thought-criminals, and traitors generally.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston debated with himself whether to award Comrade Ogilvy the Order of\"},{\"text\":\"Conspicuous Merit: in the end he decided against it because of the\"},{\"text\":\"unnecessary cross-referencing that it would entail.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the opposite cubicle. Something\"},{\"text\":\"seemed to tell him with certainty that Tillotson was busy on the same job\"},{\"text\":\"as himself. There was no way of knowing whose job would finally be adopted,\"},{\"text\":\"but he felt a profound conviction that it would be his own. Comrade Ogilvy,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"unimagined an hour ago, was now a fact. It struck him as curious that you\"},{\"text\":\"could create dead men but not living ones. Comrade Ogilvy, who had never\"},{\"text\":\"existed in the present, now existed in the past, and when once the act of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"just as authentically, and upon the\"},{\"text\":\"same evidence, as Charlemagne or Julius Caesar.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Chapter 5\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"low-ceilinged canteen, deep underground, the lunch queue jerked\"},{\"text\":\"slowly forward. The room was already very full and deafeningly noisy. From\"},{\"text\":\"the grille at the counter the steam of stew came pouring forth, with a sour\"}]","[{\"text\":\"overcome the fumes of Victory Gin. On\"},{\"text\":\"the far side of the room there was a small bar, a mere hole in the wall,\"},{\"text\":\"where gin could be bought at ten cents the large nip.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Just the man I was looking for,' said a voice at Winston's back.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He turned round. It was his friend Syme, who worked in the Research\"},{\"text\":\"Department. Perhaps 'friend' was not exactly the right word. You did not\"},{\"text\":\"have friends nowadays, you had comrades: but there were some comrades whose\"}]","[{\"text\":\"others. Syme was a philologist, a\"},{\"text\":\"specialist in Newspeak. Indeed, he was one of the enormous team of experts\"},{\"text\":\"now engaged in compiling the Eleventh Edition of the Newspeak Dictionary.\"},{\"text\":\"He was a tiny creature, smaller than Winston, with dark hair and large,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"protuberant eyes, at once mournful and derisive, which seemed to search\"},{\"text\":\"your face closely while he was speaking to you.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I wanted to ask you whether you'd got any razor blades,' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston with a sort of guilty haste. 'I've tried all over\"},{\"text\":\"the place. They don't exist any longer.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Everyone kept asking you for razor blades. Actually he had two unused ones\"}]","[{\"text\":\"been a famine of them for months past.\"},{\"text\":\"At any given moment there was some necessary article which the Party shops\"},{\"text\":\"were unable to supply. Sometimes it was buttons, sometimes it was darning\"}]","[{\"text\":\"razor blades. You could\"},{\"text\":\"only get hold of them, if at all, by scrounging more or less furtively on\"},{\"text\":\"the 'free' market.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I've been using the same blade for six weeks,' he added untruthfully.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"another jerk forward. As they halted he turned and faced\"},{\"text\":\"Syme again. Each of them took 