,{\"text\":\"would be switched off at the main at twenty-three thirty. He went into the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Then he went to\"},{\"text\":\"the table in the alcove, sat down, and took the diary out of the drawer.\"},{\"text\":\"But he did not open it at once. From the telescreen a brassy female voice\"},{\"text\":\"was squalling a patriotic song. He sat staring at the marbled cover of the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"without success to shut the voice out of his consciousness.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"It was at night that they came for you, always at night. The proper thing\"},{\"text\":\"was to kill yourself before they got you. Undoubtedly some people did so.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"disappearances were actually suicides. But it needed desperate\"},{\"text\":\"courage to kill yourself in a world where firearms, or any quick and\"},{\"text\":\"certain poison, were completely unprocurable. He thought with a kind of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"uselessness of pain and fear, the treachery\"},{\"text\":\"of the human body which always freezes into inertia at exactly the moment\"},{\"text\":\"when a special effort is needed. He might have silenced the dark-haired\"}]","[{\"text\":\"because of the\"},{\"text\":\"extremity of his danger he had lost the power to act. It struck him that\"},{\"text\":\"in moments of crisis one is never fighting against an external enemy, but\"},{\"text\":\"always against one's own body. Even now, in spite of the gin, the dull\"}]","[{\"text\":\"made consecutive thought impossible. And it is the same,\"},{\"text\":\"he perceived, in all seemingly heroic or tragic situations. On the\"},{\"text\":\"battlefield, in the torture chamber, on a sinking ship, the issues that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"body swells up until\"},{\"text\":\"it fills the universe, and even when you are not paralysed by fright or\"},{\"text\":\"screaming with pain, life is a moment-to-moment struggle against hunger or\"},{\"text\":\"cold or sleeplessness, against a sour stomach or an aching tooth.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He opened the diary. It was important to write something down. The woman\"},{\"text\":\"on the telescreen had started a new song. Her voice seemed to stick into\"},{\"text\":\"his brain like jagged splinters of glass. He tried to think of O'Brien,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"written, but instead he began thinking\"},{\"text\":\"of the things that would happen to him after the Thought Police took him\"},{\"text\":\"away. It would not matter if they killed you at once. To be killed was\"}]","[{\"text\":\"such things, yet\"},{\"text\":\"everybody knew of them) there was the routine of confession that had to\"},{\"text\":\"be gone through: the grovelling on the floor and screaming for mercy, the\"},{\"text\":\"crack of broken bones, the smashed teeth and bloody clots of hair.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Why did you have to endure it, since the end was always the same? Why was\"},{\"text\":\"it not possible to cut a few days or weeks out of your life? Nobody ever\"},{\"text\":\"escaped detection, and nobody ever failed to confess. When once you had\"}]","[{\"text\":\"certain that by a given date you would be\"},{\"text\":\"dead. Why then did that horror, which altered nothing, have to lie embedded\"},{\"text\":\"in future time?\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He tried with a little more success than before to summon up the image of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"meet in the place where there is no darkness,' O'Brien\"},{\"text\":\"had said to him. He knew what it meant, or thought he knew. The place where\"},{\"text\":\"there is no darkness was the imagined future, which one would never see,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"in. But with the\"},{\"text\":\"voice from the telescreen nagging at his ears he could not follow the train\"},{\"text\":\"of thought further. He put a cigarette in his mouth. Half the tobacco\"},{\"text\":\"promptly fell out on to his tongue, a bitter dust which was difficult to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The face of Big Brother swam into his mind, displacing that\"},{\"te