in.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"A curious emotion stirred in Winston's heart. In front of him was an enemy\"}]","[{\"text\":\"human creature,\"},{\"text\":\"in pain and perhaps with a broken bone. Already he had instinctively\"},{\"text\":\"started forward to help her. In the moment when he had seen her fall on\"},{\"text\":\"the bandaged arm, it had been as though he felt the pain in his own body.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'You're hurt?' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'It's nothing. My arm. It'll be all right in a second.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"She spoke as though her heart were fluttering. She had certainly turned\"},{\"text\":\"very pale.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"broken anything?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No, I'm all right. It hurt for a moment, that's all.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"She held out her free hand to him, and he helped her up. She had regained\"},{\"text\":\"some of her colour, and appeared very much better.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'It's nothing,' she repeated shortly. 'I only gave my wrist a bit of a\"},{\"text\":\"bang. Thanks, comrade!'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"And with that she walked on in the direction in which she had been going,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"whole incident could\"},{\"text\":\"not have taken as much as half a minute. Not to let one's feelings appear\"},{\"text\":\"in one's face was a habit that had acquired the status of an instinct,\"},{\"text\":\"and in any case they had been standing straight in front of a telescreen\"}]","[{\"text\":\"when the thing happened. Nevertheless it had been very difficult not to\"},{\"text\":\"betray a momentary surprise, for in the two or three seconds while he was\"},{\"text\":\"helping her up the girl had slipped something into his hand. There was no\"}]","[{\"text\":\"intentionally. It was something small and\"},{\"text\":\"flat. As he passed through the lavatory door he transferred it to his\"},{\"text\":\"pocket and felt it with the