},{\"text\":\"was home and in bed--in the darkness, where you were safe even from the\"},{\"text\":\"telescreen so long as you kept silent--that he was able to think\"},{\"text\":\"continuously.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"It was a physical problem that had to be solved: how to get in touch with\"},{\"text\":\"the girl and arrange a meeting. He did not consider any longer the\"},{\"text\":\"possibility that she might be laying some kind of trap for him. He knew\"}]","[{\"text\":\"unmistakable agitation when she handed\"},{\"text\":\"him the note. Obviously she had been frightened out of her wits, as well\"},{\"text\":\"she might be. Nor did the idea of refusing her advances even cross his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"her skull in with\"},{\"text\":\"a cobblestone, but that was of no importance. He thought of her naked,\"},{\"text\":\"youthful body, as he had seen it in his dream. He had imagined her a fool\"},{\"text\":\"like all the rest of them, her head stuffed with lies and hatred, her\"}]","[{\"text\":\"A kind of fever seized him at the thought that he might\"},{\"text\":\"lose her, the white youthful body might slip away from him! What he feared\"},{\"text\":\"more than anything else was that she would simply change her mind if he\"}]","[{\"text\":\"difficulty of\"},{\"text\":\"meeting was enormous. It was like trying to make a move at chess when you\"},{\"text\":\"were already mated. Whichever way you turned, the telescreen faced you.\"},{\"text\":\"Actually, all the possible ways of communicating with her had occurred to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"minutes of reading the note; but now, with time to think,\"},{\"text\":\"he went over them one by one, as though laying out a row of instruments\"},{\"text\":\"on a table.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Obviously the kind of encounter that had happened this morning could not\"}]","[{\"text\":\"be repeated. If she had worked in the Records Department it might have\"},{\"text\":\"been comparatively simple, but he had only a very dim idea whereabouts in\"},{\"text\":\"the building the Fiction Department lay, and he had no pretext for going\"}]","[{\"text\":\"lived, and at what time she left work,\"},{\"text\":\"he could have contrived to meet her somewhere on her way home; but to try\"},{\"text\":\"to follow her home was not safe, because it would mean loitering about\"}]","[{\"text\":\"for sending a\"},{\"text\":\"letter through the mails, it was out of the question. By a routine that\"},{\"text\":\"was not even secret, all letters were opened in transit. Actually, few\"},{\"text\":\"people ever wrote letters. For the messages that it was occasionally\"}]","[{\"text\":\"there were printed postcards with long lists of phrases,\"},{\"text\":\"and you struck out the ones that were inapplicable. In any case he did not\"},{\"text\":\"know the girl's name, let alone her address. Finally he decided that the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"table by herself,\"},{\"text\":\"somewhere in the middle of the room, not too near the telescreens, and\"},{\"text\":\"with a sufficient buzz of conversation all round--if these conditions\"},{\"text\":\"endured for, say, thirty seconds, it might be possible to exchange a few\"},{\"text\":\"words.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"For a week after this, life was like a restless dream. On the next day she\"},{\"text\":\"did not appear in the canteen until he was leaving it, the whistle having\"},{\"text\":\"already blown. Presumably she had been changed on to a later shift. They\"}]","[{\"text\":\"On the day after that she was in the\"},{\"text\":\"canteen at the usual time, but with three other girls and immediately\"},{\"text\":\"under a telescreen. Then for three dreadful days she did not appear at\"},{\"text\":\"all. His whole mind and body seemed to be afflicted with an unbearable\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sensitivity, a sort of transparency, which made every movement, every\"},{\"text\":\"sound, every contact, every word that he had to speak or listen to, an\"},{\"text\":\"agony. Even in sleep he could not