uld\"},{\"text\":\"never have been a time when that seemed ordinary? Julia woke up, rubbed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"oilstove.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Half that water's boiled away,' she said. 'I'll get up and make some\"},{\"text\":\"coffee in another moment. We've got an hour. What time do they cut the\"},{\"text\":\"lights off at your flats?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"thirty.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'It's twenty-three at the hostel. But you have to get in earlier than that,\"},{\"text\":\"because--Hi! Get out, you filthy brute!'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"She suddenly twisted herself over in the bed, seized a shoe from the floor,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and sent it hurtling into the corner with a boyish jerk of her arm, exactly\"},{\"text\":\"as he had seen her fling the dictionary at Goldstein, that morning during\"},{\"text\":\"the Two Minutes Hate.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'What was it?' he said in surprise.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'A rat. I saw him stick his beastly nose out of the wainscoting. There's a\"},{\"text\":\"hole down there. I gave him a good fright, anyway.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Rats!' murmured Winston. 'In this room!'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Julia indifferently as she lay down\"},{\"text\":\"again. 'We've even got them in the kitchen at the hostel. Some parts of\"},{\"text\":\"London are swarming with them. Did you know they attack children? Yes,\"},{\"text\":\"they do. In some of these streets a woman daren't leave a baby alone for\"}]","[{\"text\":\"two minutes. It's the great huge brown ones that do it. And the nasty\"},{\"text\":\"thing is that the brutes always----'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'DON'T GO ON!' said Winston, with his eyes tightly shut.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"they make you feel\"},{\"text\":\"sick?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Of all horrors in the world--a rat!'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"She pressed herself against him and wound her limbs round him, as though\"},{\"text\":\"to reassure him with the warmth of her body. He did not reopen his eyes\"}]","[{\"text\":\"immediately. For several moments he had had the feeling of being back in a\"},{\"text\":\"nightmare which had recurred from time to time throughout his life. It was\"},{\"text\":\"always very much the same. He was standing in front of a wall of darkness,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"something unendurable, something too\"},{\"text\":\"dreadful to be faced. In the dream his deepest feeling was always one of\"},{\"text\":\"self-deception, because he did in fact know what was behind the wall of\"},{\"text\":\"darkness. With a deadly effort, like wrenching a piece out of his own\"}]","[{\"text\":\"brain, he could even have dragged the thing into the open. He always woke\"},{\"text\":\"up without discovering what it was: but somehow it was connected with what\"},{\"text\":\"Julia had been saying when he cut her short.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"I don't like rats, that's all.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Don't worry, dear, we're not going to have the filthy brutes in here.\"},{\"text\":\"I'll stuff the hole with a bit of sacking before we go. And next time we\"}]","[{\"text\":\"properly.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Already the black instant of panic was half-forgotten. Feeling slightly\"},{\"text\":\"ashamed of himself, he sat up against the bedhead. Julia got out of bed,\"},{\"text\":\"pulled on her overalls, and made the coffee. The smell that rose from the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"saucepan was so powerful and exciting that they shut the window lest\"},{\"text\":\"anybody outside should notice it and become inquisitive. What was even\"},{\"text\":\"better than the taste of the coffee was the silky texture given to it by\"}]","[{\"text\":\"forgotten after years of saccharine.\"},{\"text\":\"With one hand in her pocket and a piece of bread and jam in the other,\"},{\"text\":\"Julia wandered about the room, glancing indifferently at the bookcase,\"},{\"text\":\"pointing out the best way of repairing the gateleg table, plumping herself\"}]","[{\"text\":\"down in the ragged arm-chair to see if it was comfortable, and examining\"},{\"text\":\"the absurd twelve-hour clock with a sort of tolerant amusement. She brought\"},{\"text\":\"the glass paperweight over to the bed to have a look at it in a better\"}]","[{\"text\":\"fascinated, as always, by the soft,\"},{\"text\":\"rainwatery appearance of the glass.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'What is it, do you think?' said Julia.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I don't think it's anything--I mean, I don't think it was ever put to any\"}]","[{\"text\":\"like about it. It's a little chunk of history that\"},{\"text\":\"they've forgotten to alter. It's a message from a hundred years ago, if\"},{\"text\":\"one knew how to read it.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'And that picture over there'--she nodded at the engraving on the opposite\"}]","[{\"text\":\"wall--'would that be a hundred years old?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'More. Two hundred, I dare say. One can't tell. It's impossible to discover\"},{\"text\":\"the age of anything nowadays.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"stuck his nose out,'\"},{\"text\":\"she said, kicking the wainscoting immediately below the picture. 'What is\"},{\"text\":\"this place? I've seen it before somewhere.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'It's a church, or at least it used to be. St Clement Danes its name was.'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The fragment of rhyme that Mr Charrington had taught him came back into\"},{\"text\":\"his head, and he added half-nostalgically: \\\"Oranges and lemons, say the\"},{\"text\":\"bells of St Clement's!\\\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"To his astonishment she capped the line:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'You owe me three farthings, say the bells of St Martin's,\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"hen will you pay me? say the bells of Old Bailey----'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"after that. But anyway I remember it ends\"},{\"text\":\"up, \\\"Here comes a candle to light you to bed, here comes a chopper to chop\"},{\"text\":\"off your head!\\\"'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"It was like the two halves of a countersign. But there must be another\"}]","[{\"text\":\"bells of Old Bailey'. Perhaps it could be dug out of\"},{\"text\":\"Mr Charrington's memory, if he were suitably prompted.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Who taught you that?' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'My grandfather. He used to say it to me when I was a little girl. He was\"}]","[{\"text\":\"vaporized when I was eight--at any rate, he disappeared. I wonder what a\"},{\"text\":\"lemon was,' she added inconsequently. 'I've seen oranges. They're a kind\"},{\"text\":\"of round yellow fruit with a thick skin.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston. 'They were quite common in the\"},{\"text\":\"fifties. They were so sour that it set your teeth on edge even to smell\"},{\"text\":\"them.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I bet that picture's got bugs behind it,' said Julia. 'I'll take it down\"}]","[{\"text\":\"clean some day. I suppose it's almost time we were\"},{\"text\":\"leaving. I must start washing this paint off. What a bore! I'll get the\"},{\"text\":\"lipstick off your face afterwards.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston did not get up for a few minutes more. The room was darkening. He\"}]","[{\"text\":\"turned over towards the light and lay gazing into the glass paperweight.\"},{\"text\":\"The inexhaustibly interesting thing was not the fragment of coral but the\"},{\"text\":\"interior of the glass itself. There was such a depth of it, and yet it was\"}]","[{\"text\":\"as though the surface of the glass\"},{\"text\":\"had been the arch of the sky, enclosing a tiny world with its atmosphere\"},{\"text\":\"complete. He had the feeling that he could get inside it, and that in\"},{\"text\":\"fact he was inside it, along with the mahogany bed and the gateleg table,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and the clock and the steel engraving and the paperweight itself. The\"},{\"text\":\"paperweight was the room he was in, and the coral was Julia's life and his\"},{\"text\":\"own, fixed in a sort of eternity at the heart of the crystal.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Chapter 5\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Syme had vanished. A morning came, and he was missing from work: a few\"},{\"text\":\"thoughtless people commented on his absence. On the next day nobody\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston went into the vestibule of the\"},{\"text\":\"Records Department to look at the notice-board. One of the notices carried\"},{\"text\":\"a printed list of the members of the Chess Committee, of whom Syme had\"}]","[{\"text\":\"before--nothing had\"},{\"text\":\"been crossed out--but it was one name shorter. It was enough. Syme had\"},{\"text\":\"ceased to exist: he had never existed.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The weather was baking hot. In the labyrinthine Ministry the windowless,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"air-conditioned rooms kept their normal temperature, but outside the\"},{\"text\":\"pavements scorched one's feet and the stench of the Tubes at the rush hours\"},{\"text\":\"was a horror. The preparations for Hate Week were in full swing, and the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"working overtime. Processions, meetings,\"},{\"text\":\"military parades, lectures, waxworks, displays, film shows, telescreen\"},{\"text\":\"programmes all had to be organized; stands had to be erected, effigies\"}]","[{\"text\":\"circulated, photographs\"},{\"text\":\"faked. Julia's unit in the Fiction Department had been taken off the\"},{\"text\":\"production of novels and was rushing out a series of atrocity pamphlets.\"},{\"text\":\"Winston, in addition to his regular work, spent long periods every day in\"}]","[{\"text\":\"going through back files of 'The Times' and altering and embellishing news\"},{\"text\":\"items which were to be quoted in speeches. Late at night, when crowds of\"},{\"text\":\"rowdy proles roamed the streets, the town had a curiously febrile air. The\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ever, and sometimes in the far distance\"},{\"text\":\"there were enormous explosions which no one could explain and about which\"},{\"text\":\"there were wild rumours.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The new tune which was to be the theme-song of Hate Week (the Hate Song,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"it was called) had already been composed and was being endlessly plugged\"},{\"text\":\"on the telescreens. It had a savage, barking rhythm which could not exactly\"},{\"text\":\"be called music, but resembled the beating of a drum. Roared out by\"}]","[{\"text\":\"marching feet, it was terrifying. The\"},{\"text\":\"proles had taken a fancy to it, and in the midnight streets it competed\"},{\"text\":\"with the still-popular 'It was only a hopeless fancy'. The Parsons children\"},{\"text\":\"played it at all hours of the night and day, unbearably, on a comb and a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"piece of toilet paper. Winston's evenings were fuller than ever. Squads of\"},{\"text\":\"volunteers, organized by Parsons, were preparing the street for Hate Week,\"},{\"text\":\"stitching banners, painting posters, erecting flagstaffs on the roofs, and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"street for the reception of streamers.\"},{\"text\":\"Parsons boasted that Victory Mansions alone would display four hundred\"},{\"text\":\"metres of bunting. He was in his native element and as happy as a lark.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"pretext for reverting\"},{\"text\":\"to shorts and an open shirt in the evenings. He was everywhere at once,\"},{\"text\":\"pushing, pulling, sawing, hammering, improvising, jollying everyone along\"},{\"text\":\"with comradely exhortations and giving out from every fold of his body what\"}]","[{\"text\":\"seemed an inexhaustible supply of acrid-smelling sweat.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"A new poster had suddenly appeared all over London. It had no caption,\"},{\"text\":\"and represented simply the monstrous figure of a Eurasian soldier, three\"}]","[{\"text\":\"with expressionless Mongolian face\"},{\"text\":\"and enormous boots, a submachine gun pointed from his hip. From whatever\"},{\"text\":\"angle you looked at the poster, the muzzle of the gun, magnified by the\"},{\"text\":\"foreshortening, seemed to be pointed straight at you. The thing had been\"}]","[{\"text\":\"plastered on every blank space on every wall, even outnumbering the\"},{\"text\":\"portraits of Big Brother. The proles, normally apathetic about the war,\"},{\"text\":\"were being lashed into one of their periodical frenzies of patriotism.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"general mood, the rocket bombs had been\"},{\"text\":\"killing larger numbers of people than usual. One fell on a crowded film\"},{\"text\":\"theatre in Stepney, burying several hundred victims among the ruins. The\"}]","[{\"text\":\"long, trailing\"},{\"text\":\"funeral which went on for hours and was in effect an indignation meeting.\"},{\"text\":\"Another bomb fell on a piece of waste ground which was used as a playground\"},{\"text\":\"and several dozen children were blown to pieces. There were further angry\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Goldstein was burned in effigy, hundreds of copies of the\"},{\"text\":\"poster of the Eurasian soldier were torn down and added to the flames, and\"},{\"text\":\"a number of shops were looted in the turmoil; then a rumour flew round\"}]","[{\"text\":\"bombs by means of wireless waves, and\"},{\"text\":\"an old couple who were suspected of being of foreign extraction had their\"},{\"text\":\"house set on fire and perished of suffocation.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"In the room over Mr Charrington's shop, when they could get there, Julia\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and Winston lay side by side on a stripped bed under the open window,\"},{\"text\":\"naked for the sake of coolness. The rat had never come back, but the bugs\"},{\"text\":\"had multiplied hideously in the heat. It did not seem to matter. Dirty or\"}]","[{\"text\":\"as they arrived they would sprinkle\"},{\"text\":\"everything with pepper bought on the black market, tear off their clothes,\"},{\"text\":\"and make love with sweating bodies, then fall asleep and wake to find that\"},{\"text\":\"the bugs had rallied and were massing for the counter-attack.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Four, five, six--seven times they met during the month of June. Winston\"},{\"text\":\"had dropped his habit of drinking gin at all hours. He seemed to have lost\"},{\"text\":\"the need for it. He had grown fatter, his varicose ulcer had subsided,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"skin above his ankle, his fits of\"},{\"text\":\"coughing in the early morning had stopped. The process of life had ceased\"},{\"text\":\"to be intolerable, he had no longer any impulse to make faces at the\"},{\"text\":\"telescreen or shout curses at the top of his voice. Now that they had a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"secure hiding-place, almost a home, it did not even seem a hardship that\"},{\"text\":\"they could only meet infrequently and for a couple of hours at a time.\"},{\"text\":\"What mattered was that the room over the junk-shop should exist. To know\"}]","[{\"text\":\"almost the same as being in it. The room\"},{\"text\":\"was a world, a pocket of the past where extinct animals could walk.\"},{\"text\":\"Mr Charrington, thought Winston, was another extinct animal. He usually\"}]","[{\"text\":\"his way upstairs.\"},{\"text\":\"The old man seemed seldom or never to go out of doors, and on the other\"},{\"text\":\"hand to have almost no customers. He led a ghostlike existence between the\"},{\"text\":\"tiny, dark shop, and an even tinier back kitchen where he prepared his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"contained, among other things, an unbelievably ancient\"},{\"text\":\"gramophone with an enormous horn. He seemed glad of the opportunity to\"},{\"text\":\"talk. Wandering about among his worthless stock, with his long nose and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"jacket, he had\"},{\"text\":\"always vaguely the air of being a collector rather than a tradesman.\"},{\"text\":\"With a sort of faded enthusiasm he would finger this scrap of rubbish or\"},{\"text\":\"that--a china bottle-stopper, the painted lid of a broken snuffbox, a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"containing a strand of some long-dead baby's hair--never\"},{\"text\":\"asking that Winston should buy it, merely that he should admire it. To\"},{\"text\":\"talk to him was like listening to the tinkling of a worn-out musical-box.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"more fragments of\"},{\"text\":\"forgotten rhymes. There was one about four and twenty blackbirds, and\"},{\"text\":\"another about a cow with a crumpled horn, and another about the death\"},{\"text\":\"of poor Cock Robin. 'It just occurred to me you might be interested,' he\"}]","[{\"text\":\"deprecating little laugh whenever he produced a new\"},{\"text\":\"fragment. But he could never recall more than a few lines of any one\"},{\"text\":\"rhyme.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Both of them knew--in a way, it was never out of their minds that what\"}]","[{\"text\":\"could not last long. There were times when the fact of\"},{\"text\":\"impending death seemed as palpable as the bed they lay on, and they would\"},{\"text\":\"cling together with a sort of despairing sensuality, like a damned soul\"}]","[{\"text\":\"is within five\"},{\"text\":\"minutes of striking. But there were also times when they had the illusion\"},{\"text\":\"not only of safety but of permanence. So long as they were actually in\"},{\"text\":\"this room, they both felt, no harm could come to them. Getting there was\"}]","[{\"text\":\"dangerous, but the room itself was sanctuary. It was as when\"},{\"text\":\"Winston had gazed into the heart of the paperweight, with the feeling that\"},{\"text\":\"it would be possible to get inside that glassy world, and that once inside\"}]","[{\"text\":\"gave themselves up to daydreams of\"},{\"text\":\"escape. Their luck would hold indefinitely, and they would carry on their\"},{\"text\":\"intrigue, just like this, for the remainder of their natural lives. Or\"},{\"text\":\"Katharine would die, and by subtle manoeuvrings Winston and Julia would\"}]","[{\"text\":\"succeed in getting married. Or they would commit suicide together. Or\"},{\"text\":\"they would disappear, alter themselves out of recognition, learn to speak\"},{\"text\":\"with proletarian accents, get jobs in a factory and live out their lives\"}]","[{\"text\":\"all nonsense, as they both knew. In\"},{\"text\":\"reality there was no escape. Even the one plan that was practicable,\"},{\"text\":\"suicide, they had no intention of carrying out. To hang on from day to day\"},{\"text\":\"and from week to week, spinning out a present that had no future, seemed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"an unconquerable instinct, just as one's lungs will always draw the next\"},{\"text\":\"breath so long as there is air available.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Sometimes, too, they talked of engaging in active rebellion against the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"take the first step. Even if the\"},{\"text\":\"fabulous Brotherhood was a reality, there still remained the difficulty\"},{\"text\":\"of finding one's way into it. He told her of the strange intimacy that\"},{\"text\":\"existed, or seemed to exist, between himself and O'Brien, and of the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"impulse he sometimes felt, simply to walk into O'Brien's presence, announce\"},{\"text\":\"that he was the enemy of the Party, and demand his help. Curiously enough,\"},{\"text\":\"this did not strike her as an impossibly rash thing to do. She was used to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"seemed natural to her that Winston\"},{\"text\":\"should believe O'Brien to be trustworthy on the strength of a single flash\"},{\"text\":\"of the eyes. Moreover she took it for granted that everyone, or nearly\"},{\"text\":\"everyone, secretly hated the Party and would break the rules if he thought\"}]","[{\"text\":\"it safe to do so. But she refused to believe that widespread, organized\"},{\"text\":\"opposition existed or could exist. The tales about Goldstein and his\"},{\"text\":\"underground army, she said, were simply a lot of rubbish which the Party\"}]","[{\"text\":\"which you had to pretend to believe\"},{\"text\":\"in. Times beyond number, at Party rallies and spontaneous demonstrations,\"},{\"text\":\"she had shouted at the top of her voice for the execution of people whose\"},{\"text\":\"names she had never heard and in whose supposed crimes she had not the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"faintest belief. When public trials were happening she had taken her place\"},{\"text\":\"in the detachments from the Youth League who surrounded the courts from\"},{\"text\":\"morning to night, chanting at intervals 'Death to the traitors!' During\"}]","[{\"text\":\"excelled all others in shouting insults\"},{\"text\":\"at Goldstein. Yet she had only the dimmest idea of who Goldstein was and\"},{\"text\":\"what doctrines he was supposed to represent. She had grown up since the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"battles of the\"},{\"text\":\"fifties and sixties. Such a thing as an independent political movement was\"},{\"text\":\"outside her imagination: and in any case the Party was invincible. It\"},{\"text\":\"would always exist, and it would always be the same. You could only rebel\"}]","[{\"text\":\"secret disobedience or, at most, by isolated acts of\"},{\"text\":\"violence such as killing somebody or blowing something up.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"In some ways she was far more acute than Winston, and far less susceptible\"}]","[{\"text\":\"happened in some connexion to mention\"},{\"text\":\"the war against Eurasia, she startled him by saying casually that in her\"},{\"text\":\"opinion the war was not happening. The rocket bombs which fell daily on\"},{\"text\":\"London were probably fired by the Government of Oceania itself, 'just to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"keep people frightened'. This was an idea that had literally never occurred\"},{\"text\":\"to him. She also stirred a sort of envy in him by telling him that during\"},{\"text\":\"the Two Minutes Hate her great difficulty was to avoid bursting out\"}]","[{\"text\":\"teachings of the Party when they\"},{\"text\":\"in some way touched upon her own life. Often she was ready to accept\"},{\"text\":\"the official mythology, simply because the difference between truth and\"},{\"text\":\"falsehood did not seem important to her. She believed, for instance, having\"}]","[{\"text\":\"learnt it at school, that the Party had invented aeroplanes. (In his own\"},{\"text\":\"schooldays, Winston remembered, in the late fifties, it was only the\"},{\"text\":\"helicopter that the Party claimed to have invented; a dozen years later,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"already claiming the aeroplane; one\"},{\"text\":\"generation more, and it would be claiming the steam engine.) And when he\"},{\"text\":\"told her that aeroplanes had been in existence before he was born and long\"},{\"text\":\"before the Revolution, the fact struck her as totally uninteresting. After\"}]","[{\"text\":\"all, what did it matter who had invented aeroplanes? It was rather more\"},{\"text\":\"of a shock to him when he discovered from some chance remark that she did\"},{\"text\":\"not remember that Oceania, four years ago, had been at war with Eastasia\"}]","[{\"text\":\"true that she regarded the whole war as\"},{\"text\":\"a sham: but apparently she had not even noticed that the name of the enemy\"},{\"text\":\"had changed. 'I thought we'd always been at war with Eurasia,' she said\"}]","[{\"text\":\"aeroplanes dated\"},{\"text\":\"from long before her birth, but the switchover in the war had happened\"},{\"text\":\"only four years ago, well after she was grown up. He argued with her about\"},{\"text\":\"it for perhaps a quarter of an hour. In the end he succeeded in forcing\"}]","[{\"text\":\"until she did dimly recall that at one time Eastasia and\"},{\"text\":\"not Eurasia had been the enemy. But the issue still struck her as\"},{\"text\":\"unimportant. 'Who cares?' she said impatiently. 'It's always one bloody\"}]","[{\"text\":\"anyway.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Sometimes he talked to her of the Records Department and the impudent\"},{\"text\":\"forgeries that he committed there. Such things did not appear to horrify\"},{\"text\":\"her. She did not feel the abyss opening beneath her feet at the thought\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of lies becoming truths. He told her the story of Jones, Aaronson, and\"},{\"text\":\"Rutherford and the momentous slip of paper which he had once held between\"},{\"text\":\"his fingers. It did not make much impression on her. At first, indeed, she\"}]","[{\"text\":\"story.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Were they friends of yours?' she said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No, I never knew them. They were Inner Party members. Besides, they were\"},{\"text\":\"far older men than I was. They belonged to the old days, before the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Revolution. I barely knew them by sight.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Then what was there to worry about? People are being killed off all the\"},{\"text\":\"time, aren't they?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"exceptional case. It wasn't\"},{\"text\":\"just a question of somebody being killed. Do you realize that the past,\"},{\"text\":\"starting from yesterday, has been actually abolished? If it survives\"},{\"text\":\"anywhere, it's in a few solid objects with no words attached to them, like\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that lump of glass there. Already we know almost literally nothing about\"},{\"text\":\"the Revolution and the years before the Revolution. Every record has been\"},{\"text\":\"destroyed or falsified, every book has been rewritten, every picture has\"}]","[{\"text\":\"street and building has been renamed,\"},{\"text\":\"every date has been altered. And that process is continuing day by day and\"},{\"text\":\"minute by minute. History has stopped. Nothing exists except an endless\"},{\"text\":\"present in which the Party is always right. I know, of course, that the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"past is falsified, but it would never be possible for me to prove it, even\"},{\"text\":\"when I did the falsification myself. After the thing is done, no evidence\"},{\"text\":\"ever remains. The only evidence is inside my own mind, and I don't know\"}]","[{\"text\":\"human being shares my memories. Just in\"},{\"text\":\"that one instance, in my whole life, I did possess actual concrete evidence\"},{\"text\":\"after the event--years after it.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'And what good was that?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"because I threw it away a few minutes later. But if the\"},{\"text\":\"same thing happened today, I should keep it.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Well, I wouldn't!' said Julia. 'I'm quite ready to take risks, but only\"}]","[{\"text\":\"newspaper. What could you\"},{\"text\":\"have done with it even if you had kept it?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Not much, perhaps. But it was evidence. It might have planted a few doubts\"},{\"text\":\"here and there, supposing that I'd dared to show it to anybody. I don't\"}]","[{\"text\":\"imagine that we can alter anything in our own lifetime. But one can imagine\"},{\"text\":\"little knots of resistance springing up here and there--small groups of\"},{\"text\":\"people banding themselves together, and gradually growing, and even leaving\"}]","[{\"text\":\"next generations can carry on where we\"},{\"text\":\"leave off.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I'm not interested in the next generation, dear. I'm interested in US.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You're only a rebel from the waist downwards,' he told her.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"She thought this brilliantly witty and flung her arms round him in delight.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"In the ramifications of party doctrine she had not the faintest interest.\"},{\"text\":\"Whenever he began to talk of the principles of Ingsoc, doublethink, the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"past, and the denial of objective reality, and to use\"},{\"text\":\"Newspeak words, she became bored and confused and said that she never paid\"},{\"text\":\"any attention to that kind of thing. One knew that it was all rubbish, so\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and when to boo,\"},{\"text\":\"and that was all one needed. If he persisted in talking of such subjects,\"},{\"text\":\"she had a disconcerting habit of falling asleep. She was one of those\"},{\"text\":\"people who can go to sleep at any hour and in any position. Talking to her,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"easy it was to present an appearance of orthodoxy while\"},{\"text\":\"having no grasp whatever of what orthodoxy meant. In a way, the world-view\"},{\"text\":\"of the Party imposed itself most successfully on people incapable of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"flagrant violations\"},{\"text\":\"of reality, because they never fully grasped the enormity of what was\"},{\"text\":\"demanded of them, and were not sufficiently interested in public events to\"},{\"text\":\"notice what was happening. By lack of understanding they remained sane.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"They simply swallowed everything, and what they swallowed did them no harm,\"},{\"text\":\"because it left no residue behind, just as a grain of corn will pass\"},{\"text\":\"undigested through the body of a bird.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Chapter 6\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"It had happened at last. The expected message had come. All his life, it\"},{\"text\":\"seemed to him, he had been waiting for this to happen.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"at the Ministry and he was almost\"},{\"text\":\"at the spot where Julia had slipped the note into his hand when he became\"},{\"text\":\"aware that someone larger than himself was walking just behind him. The\"},{\"text\":\"person, whoever it was, gave a small cough, evidently as a prelude to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"speaking. Winston stopped abruptly and turned. It was O'Brien.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"At last they were face to face, and it seemed that his only impulse was\"},{\"text\":\"to run away. His heart bounded violently. He would have been incapable of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"however, had continued forward in the same movement,\"},{\"text\":\"laying a friendly hand for a moment on Winston's arm, so that the two of\"},{\"text\":\"them were walking side by side. He began speaking with the peculiar grave\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Inner Party members.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I had been hoping for an opportunity of talking to you,' he said. 'I was\"},{\"text\":\"reading one of your Newspeak articles in 'The Times' the other day. You\"},{\"text\":\"take a scholarly interest in Newspeak, I believe?'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston had recovered part of his self-possession. 'Hardly scholarly,' he\"},{\"text\":\"said. 'I'm only an amateur. It's not my subject. I have never had anything\"},{\"text\":\"to do with the actual construction of the language.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"said O'Brien. 'That is not only my own\"},{\"text\":\"opinion. I was talking recently to a friend of yours who is certainly an\"},{\"text\":\"expert. His name has slipped my memory for the moment.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"inconceivable that this\"},{\"text\":\"was anything other than a reference to Syme. But Syme was not only dead,\"},{\"text\":\"he was abolished, an unperson. Any identifiable reference to him would have\"},{\"text\":\"been mortally dangerous. O'Brien's remark must obviously have been intended\"}]","[{\"text\":\"as a signal, a codeword. By sharing a small act of thoughtcrime he had\"},{\"text\":\"turned the two of them into accomplices. They had continued to stroll\"},{\"text\":\"slowly down the corridor, but now O'Brien halted. With the curious,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"managed to put in to the gesture he\"},{\"text\":\"resettled his spectacles on his nose. Then he went on:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'What I had really intended to say was that in your article I noticed you\"},{\"text\":\"had used two words which have become obsolete. But they have only become\"}]","[{\"text\":\"so very recently. Have you seen the tenth edition of the Newspeak\"},{\"text\":\"Dictionary?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No,' said Winston. 'I didn't think it had been issued yet. We are still\"},{\"text\":\"using the ninth in the Records Department.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'The tenth edition is not due to appear for some months, I believe. But a\"},{\"text\":\"few advance copies have been circulated. I have one myself. It might\"},{\"text\":\"interest you to look at it, perhaps?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"this tended.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Some of the new developments are most ingenious. The reduction in the\"},{\"text\":\"number of verbs--that is the point that will appeal to you, I think. Let\"},{\"text\":\"me see, shall I send a messenger to you with the dictionary? But I am\"}]","[{\"text\":\"afraid I invariably forget anything of that kind. Perhaps you could pick\"},{\"text\":\"it up at my flat at some time that suited you? Wait. Let me give you my\"},{\"text\":\"address.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"They were standing in front of a telescreen. Somewhat absent-mindedly\"}]","[{\"text\":\"O'Brien felt two of his pockets and then produced a small leather-covered\"},{\"text\":\"notebook and a gold ink-pencil. Immediately beneath the telescreen, in\"},{\"text\":\"such a position that anyone who was watching at the other end of the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"writing, he scribbled an address, tore\"},{\"text\":\"out the page and handed it to Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I am usually at home in the evenings,' he said. 'If not, my servant will\"},{\"text\":\"give you the dictionary.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He was gone, leaving Winston holding the scrap of paper, which this time\"},{\"text\":\"there was no need to conceal. Nevertheless he carefully memorized what was\"},{\"text\":\"written on it, and some hours later dropped it into the memory hole along\"},{\"text\":\"with a mass of other papers.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"They had been talking to one another for a couple of minutes at the most.\"},{\"text\":\"There was only one meaning that the episode could possibly have. It had\"},{\"text\":\"been contrived as a way of letting Winston know O'Brien's address. This\"}]","[{\"text\":\"direct enquiry it was never possible to\"},{\"text\":\"discover where anyone lived. There were no directories of any kind. 'If\"},{\"text\":\"you ever want to see me, this is where I can be found,' was what O'Brien\"}]","[{\"text\":\"message concealed\"},{\"text\":\"somewhere in the dictionary. But at any rate, one thing was certain. The\"},{\"text\":\"conspiracy that he had dreamed of did exist, and he had reached the outer\"},{\"text\":\"edges of it.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"summons. Perhaps\"},{\"text\":\"tomorrow, perhaps after a long delay--he was not certain. What was\"},{\"text\":\"happening was only the working-out of a process that had started years\"},{\"text\":\"ago. The first step had been a secret, involuntary thought, the second\"}]","[{\"text\":\"opening of the diary. He had moved from thoughts to words,\"},{\"text\":\"and now from words to actions. The last step was something that would\"},{\"text\":\"happen in the Ministry of Love. He had accepted it. The end was contained\"}]","[{\"text\":\"frightening: or, more exactly, it was like\"},{\"text\":\"a foretaste of death, like being a little less alive. Even while he was\"},{\"text\":\"speaking to O'Brien, when the meaning of the words had sunk in, a chilly\"}]","[{\"text\":\"had the sensation\"},{\"text\":\"of stepping into the dampness of a grave, and it was not much better\"},{\"text\":\"because he had always known that the grave was there and waiting for him.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Chapter 7\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston had woken up with his eyes full of tears. Julia rolled sleepily\"},{\"text\":\"against him, murmuring something that might have been 'What's the matter?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I dreamt--' he began, and stopped short. It was too complex to be put\"}]","[{\"text\":\"was the dream itself, and there was a memory connected\"},{\"text\":\"with it that had swum into his mind in the few seconds after waking.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He lay back with his eyes shut, still sodden in the atmosphere of the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"in which his whole life seemed to\"},{\"text\":\"stretch out before him like a landscape on a summer evening after rain.\"},{\"text\":\"It had all occurred inside the glass paperweight, but the surface of the\"},{\"text\":\"glass was the dome of the sky, and inside the dome everything was flooded\"}]","[{\"text\":\"with clear soft light in which one could see into interminable distances.\"},{\"text\":\"The dream had also been comprehended by--indeed, in some sense it had\"},{\"text\":\"consisted in--a gesture of the arm made by his mother, and made again\"}]","[{\"text\":\"woman he had seen on the news film,\"},{\"text\":\"trying to shelter the small boy from the bullets, before the helicopter\"},{\"text\":\"blew them both to pieces.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Do you know,' he said, 'that until this moment I believed I had murdered\"},{\"text\":\"my mother?'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Why did you murder her?' said Julia, almost asleep.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I didn't murder her. Not physically.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"In the dream he had remembered his last glimpse of his mother, and within\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of small events surrounding it had all\"},{\"text\":\"come back. It was a memory that he must have deliberately pushed out of\"},{\"text\":\"his consciousness over many years. He was not certain of the date, but he\"}]","[{\"text\":\"twelve, when it had\"},{\"text\":\"happened.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"His father had disappeared some time earlier, how much earlier he could\"},{\"text\":\"not remember. He remembered better the rackety, uneasy circumstances of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"air-raids and the sheltering in Tube\"},{\"text\":\"stations, the piles of rubble everywhere, the unintelligible proclamations\"},{\"text\":\"posted at street corners, the gangs of youths in shirts all the same\"},{\"text\":\"colour, the enormous queues outside the bakeries, the intermittent\"}]","[{\"text\":\"machine-gun fire in the distance--above all, the fact that there was\"},{\"text\":\"never enough to eat. He remembered long afternoons spent with other boys\"},{\"text\":\"in scrounging round dustbins and rubbish heaps, picking out the ribs of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sometimes even scraps of stale breadcrust\"},{\"text\":\"from which they carefully scraped away the cinders; and also in waiting\"},{\"text\":\"for the passing of trucks which travelled over a certain route and were\"}]","[{\"text\":\"over the bad\"},{\"text\":\"patches in the road, sometimes spilt a few fragments of oil-cake.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"When his father disappeared, his mother did not show any surprise or any\"},{\"text\":\"violent grief, but a sudden change came over her. She seemed to have\"}]","[{\"text\":\"become completely spiritless. It was evident even to Winston that she was\"},{\"text\":\"waiting for something that she knew must happen. She did everything that\"},{\"text\":\"was needed--cooked, washed, mended, made the bed, swept the floor, dusted\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and with a curious lack of superfluous\"},{\"text\":\"motion, like an artist's lay-figure moving of its own accord. Her large\"},{\"text\":\"shapely body seemed to relapse naturally into stillness. For hours at a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"his young sister,\"},{\"text\":\"a tiny, ailing, very silent child of two or three, with a face made simian\"},{\"text\":\"by thinness. Very occasionally she would take Winston in her arms and\"},{\"text\":\"press him against her for a long time without saying anything. He was\"}]","[{\"text\":\"his youthfulness and selfishness, that this was somehow\"},{\"text\":\"connected with the never-mentioned thing that was about to happen.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He remembered the room where they lived, a dark, close-smelling room that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"white counterpane. There was a gas ring\"},{\"text\":\"in the fender, and a shelf where food was kept, and on the landing outside\"},{\"text\":\"there was a brown earthenware sink, common to several rooms. He remembered\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to stir at something\"},{\"text\":\"in a saucepan. Above all he remembered his continuous hunger, and the\"},{\"text\":\"fierce sordid battles at mealtimes. He would ask his mother naggingly,\"},{\"text\":\"over and over again, why there was not more food, he would shout and storm\"}]","[{\"text\":\"at her (he even remembered the tones of his voice, which was beginning to\"},{\"text\":\"break prematurely and sometimes boomed in a peculiar way), or he would\"},{\"text\":\"attempt a snivelling note of pathos in his efforts to get more than his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"give him more than his share. She\"},{\"text\":\"took it for granted that he, 'the boy', should have the biggest portion;\"},{\"text\":\"but however much she gave him he invariably demanded more. At every meal\"},{\"text\":\"she would beseech him not to be selfish and to remember that his little\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sister was sick and also needed food, but it was no use. He would cry out\"},{\"text\":\"with rage when she stopped ladling, he would try to wrench the saucepan\"},{\"text\":\"and spoon out of her hands, he would grab bits from his sister's plate.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"other two, but he could not help it; he\"},{\"text\":\"even felt that he had a right to do it. The clamorous hunger in his belly\"},{\"text\":\"seemed to justify him. Between meals, if his mother did not stand guard,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"food on the shelf.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"One day a chocolate ration was issued. There had been no such issue for\"},{\"text\":\"weeks or months past. He remembered quite clearly that precious little\"},{\"text\":\"morsel of chocolate. It was a two-ounce slab (they still talked about\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ounces in those days) between the three of them. It was obvious that it\"},{\"text\":\"ought to be divided into three equal parts. Suddenly, as though he were\"},{\"text\":\"listening to somebody else, Winston heard himself demanding in a loud\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the whole piece. His mother told him\"},{\"text\":\"not to be greedy. There was a long, nagging argument that went round and\"},{\"text\":\"round, with shouts, whines, tears, remonstrances, bargainings. His tiny\"},{\"text\":\"sister, clinging to her mother with both hands, exactly like a baby monkey,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sat looking over her shoulder at him with large, mournful eyes. In the\"},{\"text\":\"end his mother broke off three-quarters of the chocolate and gave it to\"},{\"text\":\"Winston, giving the other quarter to his sister. The little girl took hold\"}]","[{\"text\":\"not knowing what it was. Winston\"},{\"text\":\"stood watching her for a moment. Then with a sudden swift spring he had\"},{\"text\":\"snatched the piece of chocolate out of his sister's hand and was fleeing\"},{\"text\":\"for the door.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"after him. 'Come back! Give your\"},{\"text\":\"sister back her chocolate!'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He stopped, but did not come back. His mother's anxious eyes were fixed on\"},{\"text\":\"his face. Even now he was thinking about the thing, he did not know what\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the point of happening. His sister, conscious of having\"},{\"text\":\"been robbed of something, had set up a feeble wail. His mother drew her\"},{\"text\":\"arm round the child and pressed its face against her breast. Something in\"}]","[{\"text\":\"turned and fled down\"},{\"text\":\"the stairs, with the chocolate growing sticky in his hand.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He never saw his mother again. After he had devoured the chocolate he felt\"}]","[{\"text\":\"streets for several\"},{\"text\":\"hours, until hunger drove him home. When he came back his mother had\"},{\"text\":\"disappeared. This was already becoming normal at that time. Nothing was\"},{\"text\":\"gone from the room except his mother and his sister. They had not taken\"}]","[{\"text\":\"any clothes, not even his mother's overcoat. To this day he did not know\"},{\"text\":\"with any certainty that his mother was dead. It was perfectly possible\"},{\"text\":\"that she had merely been sent to a forced-labour camp. As for his sister,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston himself, to one of the colonies\"},{\"text\":\"for homeless children (Reclamation Centres, they were called) which had\"},{\"text\":\"grown up as a result of the civil war, or she might have been sent to the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"somewhere or other\"},{\"text\":\"to die.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The dream was still vivid in his mind, especially the enveloping protecting\"},{\"text\":\"gesture of the arm in which its whole meaning seemed to be contained. His\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Exactly as his mother\"},{\"text\":\"had sat on the dingy white-quilted bed, with the child clinging to her, so\"},{\"text\":\"she had sat in the sunken ship, far underneath him, and drowning deeper\"},{\"text\":\"every minute, but still looking up at him through the darkening water.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He told Julia the story of his mother's disappearance. Without opening her\"},{\"text\":\"eyes she rolled over and settled herself into a more comfortable position.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I expect you were a beastly little swine in those days,' she said\"}]","[{\"text\":\"children are swine.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes. But the real point of the story----'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"From her breathing it was evident that she was going off to sleep again.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"mother. He did not\"},{\"text\":\"suppose, from what he could remember of her, that she had been an unusual\"},{\"text\":\"woman, still less an intelligent one; and yet she had possessed a kind of\"},{\"text\":\"nobility, a kind of purity, simply because the standards that she obeyed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Her feelings were her own, and could not be altered\"},{\"text\":\"from outside. It would not have occurred to her that an action which is\"},{\"text\":\"ineffectual thereby becomes meaningless. If you loved someone, you loved\"}]","[{\"text\":\"gave him love. When\"},{\"text\":\"the last of the chocolate was gone, his mother had clasped the child in\"},{\"text\":\"her arms. It was no use, it changed nothing, it did not produce more\"},{\"text\":\"chocolate, it did not avert the child's death or her own; but it seemed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"natural to her to do it. The refugee woman in the boat had also covered\"},{\"text\":\"the little boy with her arm, which was no more use against the bullets\"},{\"text\":\"than a sheet of paper. The terrible thing that the Party had done was to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"feelings, were of no account, while\"},{\"text\":\"at the same time robbing you of all power over the material world. When\"},{\"text\":\"once you were in the grip of the Party, what you felt or did not feel,\"},{\"text\":\"what you did or refrained from doing, made literally no difference.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Whatever happened you vanished, and neither you nor your actions were ever\"},{\"text\":\"heard of again. You were lifted clean out of the stream of history. And\"},{\"text\":\"yet to the people of only two generations ago this would not have seemed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"attempting to alter history. They\"},{\"text\":\"were governed by private loyalties which they did not question. What\"},{\"text\":\"mattered were individual relationships, and a completely helpless gesture,\"},{\"text\":\"an embrace, a tear, a word spoken to a dying man, could have value in\"}]","[{\"text\":\"itself. The proles, it suddenly occurred to him, had remained in this\"},{\"text\":\"condition. They were not loyal to a party or a country or an idea, they\"},{\"text\":\"were loyal to one another. For the first time in his life he did not\"}]","[{\"text\":\"merely as an inert force which would\"},{\"text\":\"one day spring to life and regenerate the world. The proles had stayed\"},{\"text\":\"human. They had not become hardened inside. They had held on to the\"},{\"text\":\"primitive emotions which he himself had to re-learn by conscious effort.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"And in thinking this he remembered, without apparent relevance, how a few\"},{\"text\":\"weeks ago he had seen a severed hand lying on the pavement and had kicked\"},{\"text\":\"it into the gutter as though it had been a cabbage-stalk.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"human beings,' he said aloud. 'We are not human.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Why not?' said Julia, who had woken up again.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He thought for a little while. 'Has it ever occurred to you,' he said,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"would be simply to walk out of here\"},{\"text\":\"before it's too late, and never see each other again?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes, dear, it has occurred to me, several times. But I'm not going to do\"},{\"text\":\"it, all the same.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"can't last much longer. You're young.\"},{\"text\":\"You look normal and innocent. If you keep clear of people like me, you\"},{\"text\":\"might stay alive for another fifty years.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No. I've thought it all out. What you do, I'm going to do. And don't be\"}]","[{\"text\":\"too downhearted. I'm rather good at staying alive.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'We may be together for another six months--a year--there's no knowing.\"},{\"text\":\"At the end we're certain to be apart. Do you realize how utterly alone we\"}]","[{\"text\":\"us there will be nothing, literally\"},{\"text\":\"nothing, that either of us can do for the other. If I confess, they'll\"},{\"text\":\"shoot you, and if I refuse to confess, they'll shoot you just the same.\"},{\"text\":\"Nothing that I can do or say, or stop myself from saying, will put off\"}]","[{\"text\":\"your death for as much as five minutes. Neither of us will even know\"},{\"text\":\"whether the other is alive or dead. We shall be utterly without power of\"},{\"text\":\"any kind. The one thing that matters is that we shouldn't betray one\"}]","[{\"text\":\"make the slightest difference.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'If you mean confessing,' she said, 'we shall do that, right enough.\"},{\"text\":\"Everybody always confesses. You can't help it. They torture you.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"is not betrayal. What you say or do\"},{\"text\":\"doesn't matter: only feelings matter. If they could make me stop loving\"},{\"text\":\"you--that would be the real betrayal.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"She thought it over. 'They can't do that,' she said finally. 'It's the one\"}]","[{\"text\":\"thing they can't do. They can make you say anything--ANYTHING--but they\"},{\"text\":\"can't make you believe it. They can't get inside you.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No,' he said a little more hopefully, 'no; that's quite true. They can't\"}]","[{\"text\":\"staying human is worth while, even\"},{\"text\":\"when it can't have any result whatever, you've beaten them.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He thought of the telescreen with its never-sleeping ear. They could spy\"}]","[{\"text\":\"could still outwit\"},{\"text\":\"them. With all their cleverness they had never mastered the secret of\"},{\"text\":\"finding out what another human being was thinking. Perhaps that was less\"},{\"text\":\"true when you were actually in their hands. One did not know what happened\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Ministry of Love, but it was possible to guess: tortures, drugs,\"},{\"text\":\"delicate instruments that registered your nervous reactions, gradual\"},{\"text\":\"wearing-down by sleeplessness and solitude and persistent questioning.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"hidden. They could be tracked down\"},{\"text\":\"by enquiry, they could be squeezed out of you by torture. But if the object\"},{\"text\":\"was not to stay alive but to stay human, what difference did it ultimately\"},{\"text\":\"make? They could not alter your feelings: for that matter you could not\"}]","[{\"text\":\"alter them yourself, even if you wanted to. They could lay bare in the\"},{\"text\":\"utmost detail everything that you had done or said or thought; but the\"},{\"text\":\"inner heart, whose workings were mysterious even to yourself, remained\"},{\"text\":\"impregnable.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Chapter 8\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"They had done it, they had done it at last!\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The room they were standing in was long-shaped and softly lit. The\"}]","[{\"text\":\"murmur; the richness of the dark-blue carpet\"},{\"text\":\"gave one the impression of treading on velvet. At the far end of the room\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien was sitting at a table under a green-shaded lamp, with a mass of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"look up when the\"},{\"text\":\"servant showed Julia and Winston in.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston's heart was thumping so hard that he doubted whether he would be\"},{\"text\":\"able to speak. They had done it, they had done it at last, was all he\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to come here at all, and sheer folly\"},{\"text\":\"to arrive together; though it was true that they had come by different\"},{\"text\":\"routes and only met on O'Brien's doorstep. But merely to walk into such a\"},{\"text\":\"place needed an effort of the nerve. It was only on very rare occasions\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that one saw inside the dwelling-places of the Inner Party, or even\"},{\"text\":\"penetrated into the quarter of the town where they lived. The whole\"},{\"text\":\"atmosphere of the huge block of flats, the richness and spaciousness of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"good food and good tobacco, the\"},{\"text\":\"silent and incredibly rapid lifts sliding up and down, the white-jacketed\"},{\"text\":\"servants hurrying to and fro--everything was intimidating. Although he had\"},{\"text\":\"a good pretext for coming here, he was haunted at every step by the fear\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that a black-uniformed guard would suddenly appear from round the corner,\"},{\"text\":\"demand his papers, and order him to get out. O'Brien's servant, however,\"},{\"text\":\"had admitted the two of them without demur. He was a small, dark-haired\"}]","[{\"text\":\"diamond-shaped, completely expressionless\"},{\"text\":\"face which might have been that of a Chinese. The passage down which he\"},{\"text\":\"led them was softly carpeted, with cream-papered walls and white\"}]","[{\"text\":\"intimidating. Winston\"},{\"text\":\"could not remember ever to have seen a passageway whose walls were not\"},{\"text\":\"grimy from the contact of human bodies.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien had a slip of paper between his fingers and seemed to be studying\"}]","[{\"text\":\"it intently. His heavy face, bent down so that one could see the line of\"},{\"text\":\"the nose, looked both formidable and intelligent. For perhaps twenty\"},{\"text\":\"seconds he sat without stirring. Then he pulled the speakwrite towards\"}]","[{\"text\":\"hybrid jargon of the Ministries:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Items one comma five comma seven approved fullwise stop suggestion\"},{\"text\":\"contained item six doubleplus ridiculous verging crimethink cancel stop\"}]","[{\"text\":\"estimates machinery\"},{\"text\":\"overheads stop end message.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He rose deliberately from his chair and came towards them across the\"},{\"text\":\"soundless carpet. A little of the official atmosphere seemed to have fallen\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the Newspeak words, but his expression was grimmer than\"},{\"text\":\"usual, as though he were not pleased at being disturbed. The terror that\"},{\"text\":\"Winston already felt was suddenly shot through by a streak of ordinary\"}]","[{\"text\":\"had simply made a\"},{\"text\":\"stupid mistake. For what evidence had he in reality that O'Brien was any\"},{\"text\":\"kind of political conspirator? Nothing but a flash of the eyes and a single\"},{\"text\":\"equivocal remark: beyond that, only his own secret imaginings, founded on\"}]","[{\"text\":\"not even fall back on the pretence that he had come to\"},{\"text\":\"borrow the dictionary, because in that case Julia's presence was impossible\"},{\"text\":\"to explain. As O'Brien passed the telescreen a thought seemed to strike\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the wall. There was\"},{\"text\":\"a sharp snap. The voice had stopped.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Julia uttered a tiny sound, a sort of squeak of surprise. Even in the midst\"},{\"text\":\"of his panic, Winston was too much taken aback to be able to hold his\"},{\"text\":\"tongue.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'You can turn it off!' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes,' said O'Brien, 'we can turn it off. We have that privilege.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He was opposite them now. His solid form towered over the pair of them,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"still indecipherable. He was waiting,\"},{\"text\":\"somewhat sternly, for Winston to speak, but about what? Even now it was\"},{\"text\":\"quite conceivable that he was simply a busy man wondering irritably why he\"},{\"text\":\"had been interrupted. Nobody spoke. After the stopping of the telescreen\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the room seemed deadly silent. The seconds marched past, enormous. With\"},{\"text\":\"difficulty Winston continued to keep his eyes fixed on O'Brien's. Then\"},{\"text\":\"suddenly the grim face broke down into what might have been the beginnings\"}]","[{\"text\":\"gesture O'Brien resettled his\"},{\"text\":\"spectacles on his nose.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Shall I say it, or will you?' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I will say it,' said Winston promptly. 'That thing is really turned off?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Yes, everything is turned off. We are alone.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'We have come here because----'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He paused, realizing for the first time the vagueness of\"},{\"text\":\"his own motives. Since he did not in fact know what kind of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"help he expected from O'Brien, it was not easy to say why he\"},{\"text\":\"had come here. He went on, conscious that what he was saying\"},{\"text\":\"must sound both feeble and pretentious:\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of conspiracy, some kind of secret\"},{\"text\":\"organization working against the Party, and that you are involved in it.\"},{\"text\":\"We want to join it and work for it. We are enemies of the Party. We\"},{\"text\":\"disbelieve in the principles of Ingsoc. We are thought-criminals. We are\"}]","[{\"text\":\"also adulterers. I tell you this because we want to put ourselves at your\"},{\"text\":\"mercy. If you want us to incriminate ourselves in any other way, we are\"},{\"text\":\"ready.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He stopped and glanced over his shoulder, with the feeling that the door\"}]","[{\"text\":\"had opened. Sure enough, the little yellow-faced servant had come in\"},{\"text\":\"without knocking. Winston saw that he was carrying a tray with a decanter\"},{\"text\":\"and glasses.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Martin is one of us,' said O'Brien impassively. 'Bring the drinks over\"}]","[{\"text\":\"here, Martin. Put them on the round table. Have we enough chairs? Then\"},{\"text\":\"we may as well sit down and talk in comfort. Bring a chair for yourself,\"},{\"text\":\"Martin. This is business. You can stop being a servant for the next ten\"},{\"text\":\"minutes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The little man sat down, quite at his ease, and yet still with a\"},{\"text\":\"servant-like air, the air of a valet enjoying a privilege. Winston\"},{\"text\":\"regarded him out of the corner of his eye. It struck him that the man's\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that he felt it to be dangerous to\"},{\"text\":\"drop his assumed personality even for a moment. O'Brien took the decanter\"},{\"text\":\"by the neck and filled up the glasses with a dark-red liquid. It aroused\"},{\"text\":\"in Winston dim memories of something seen long ago on a wall or a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"hoarding--a vast bottle composed of electric lights which seemed to move\"},{\"text\":\"up and down and pour its contents into a glass. Seen from the top the\"},{\"text\":\"stuff looked almost black, but in the decanter it gleamed like a ruby.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Julia pick up her glass and sniff at\"},{\"text\":\"it with frank curiosity.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'It is called wine,' said O'Brien with a faint smile. 'You will have read\"},{\"text\":\"about it in books, no doubt. Not much of it gets to the Outer Party, I am\"}]","[{\"text\":\"grew solemn again, and he raised his glass: 'I think it\"},{\"text\":\"is fitting that we should begin by drinking a health. To our Leader: To\"},{\"text\":\"Emmanuel Goldstein.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston took up his glass with a certain eagerness. Wine was a thing he\"}]","[{\"text\":\"had read and dreamed about. Like the glass paperweight or Mr Charrington's\"},{\"text\":\"half-remembered rhymes, it belonged to the vanished, romantic past, the\"},{\"text\":\"olden time as he liked to call it in his secret thoughts. For some reason\"}]","[{\"text\":\"having an intensely sweet taste, like\"},{\"text\":\"that of blackberry jam and an immediate intoxicating effect. Actually,\"},{\"text\":\"when he came to swallow it, the stuff was distinctly disappointing. The\"},{\"text\":\"truth was that after years of gin-drinking he could barely taste it. He\"}]","[{\"text\":\"set down the empty glass.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Then there is such a person as Goldstein?' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes, there is such a person, and he is alive. Where, I do not know.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"organization? Is it real? It is not simply an\"},{\"text\":\"invention of the Thought Police?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No, it is real. The Brotherhood, we call it. You will never learn much\"},{\"text\":\"more about the Brotherhood than that it exists and that you belong to it.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"I will come back to that presently.' He looked at his wrist-watch. 'It is\"},{\"text\":\"unwise even for members of the Inner Party to turn off the telescreen for\"},{\"text\":\"more than half an hour. You ought not to have come here together, and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"You, comrade'--he bowed his head to\"},{\"text\":\"Julia--'will leave first. We have about twenty minutes at our disposal.\"},{\"text\":\"You will understand that I must start by asking you certain questions.\"},{\"text\":\"In general terms, what are you prepared to do?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Anything that we are capable of,' said Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien had turned himself a little in his chair so that he was facing\"},{\"text\":\"Winston. He almost ignored Julia, seeming to take it for granted that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"moment the lids flitted down over his\"},{\"text\":\"eyes. He began asking his questions in a low, expressionless voice, as\"},{\"text\":\"though this were a routine, a sort of catechism, most of whose answers\"},{\"text\":\"were known to him already.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to give your lives?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You are prepared to commit murder?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'To commit acts of sabotage which may cause the death of hundreds of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"innocent people?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'To betray your country to foreign powers?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You are prepared to cheat, to forge, to blackmail, to corrupt the minds\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of children, to distribute habit-forming drugs, to encourage prostitution,\"},{\"text\":\"to disseminate venereal diseases--to do anything which is likely to cause\"},{\"text\":\"demoralization and weaken the power of the Party?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'If, for example, it would somehow serve our interests to throw sulphuric\"},{\"text\":\"acid in a child's face--are you prepared to do that?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You are prepared to lose your identity and live out the rest of your life\"}]","[{\"text\":\"as a waiter or a dock-worker?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You are prepared to commit suicide, if and when we order you to do so?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"separate and never see one another\"},{\"text\":\"again?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No!' broke in Julia.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"It appeared to Winston that a long time passed before he answered. For a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of speech. His\"},{\"text\":\"tongue worked soundlessly, forming the opening syllables first of one word,\"},{\"text\":\"then of the other, over and over again. Until he had said it, he did not\"},{\"text\":\"know which word he was going to say. 'No,' he said finally.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'You did well to tell me,' said O'Brien. 'It is necessary for us to know\"},{\"text\":\"everything.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He turned himself toward Julia and added in a voice with somewhat more\"},{\"text\":\"expression in it:\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"survives, it may be as a different\"},{\"text\":\"person? We may be obliged to give him a new identity. His face, his\"},{\"text\":\"movements, the shape of his hands, the colour of his hair--even his voice\"},{\"text\":\"would be different. And you yourself might have become a different person.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Our surgeons can alter people beyond recognition. Sometimes it is\"},{\"text\":\"necessary. Sometimes we even amputate a limb.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston could not help snatching another sidelong glance at Martin's\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that he could see. Julia had turned a\"},{\"text\":\"shade paler, so that her freckles were showing, but she faced O'Brien\"},{\"text\":\"boldly. She murmured something that seemed to be assent.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Good. Then that is settled.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"box of cigarettes on the table. With a rather\"},{\"text\":\"absent-minded air O'Brien pushed them towards the others, took one himself,\"},{\"text\":\"then stood up and began to pace slowly to and fro, as though he could think\"}]","[{\"text\":\"thick and\"},{\"text\":\"well-packed, with an unfamiliar silkiness in the paper. O'Brien looked at\"},{\"text\":\"his wrist-watch again.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You had better go back to your Pantry, Martin,' he said. 'I shall switch\"}]","[{\"text\":\"good look at these comrades' faces\"},{\"text\":\"before you go. You will be seeing them again. I may not.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Exactly as they had done at the front door, the little man's dark eyes\"}]","[{\"text\":\"friendliness in his\"},{\"text\":\"manner. He was memorizing their appearance, but he felt no interest in\"},{\"text\":\"them, or appeared to feel none. It occurred to Winston that a synthetic\"},{\"text\":\"face was perhaps incapable of changing its expression. Without speaking\"}]","[{\"text\":\"or giving any kind of salutation, Martin went out, closing the door\"},{\"text\":\"silently behind him. O'Brien was strolling up and down, one hand in the\"},{\"text\":\"pocket of his black overalls, the other holding his cigarette.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"he said, 'that you will be fighting in the dark. You\"},{\"text\":\"will always be in the dark. You will receive orders and you will obey them,\"},{\"text\":\"without knowing why. Later I shall send you a book from which you will\"}]","[{\"text\":\"strategy by which\"},{\"text\":\"we shall destroy it. When you have read the book, you will be full members\"},{\"text\":\"of the Brotherhood. But between the general aims that we are fighting for\"},{\"text\":\"and the immediate tasks of the moment, you will never know anything. I\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Brotherhood exists, but I cannot tell you whether it\"},{\"text\":\"numbers a hundred members, or ten million. From your personal knowledge\"},{\"text\":\"you will never be able to say that it numbers even as many as a dozen. You\"}]","[{\"text\":\"from time to time as\"},{\"text\":\"they disappear. As this was your first contact, it will be preserved. When\"},{\"text\":\"you receive orders, they will come from me. If we find it necessary to\"},{\"text\":\"communicate with you, it will be through Martin. When you are finally\"}]","[{\"text\":\"caught, you will confess. That is unavoidable. But you will have very\"},{\"text\":\"little to confess, other than your own actions. You will not be able to\"},{\"text\":\"betray more than a handful of unimportant people. Probably you will not\"}]","[{\"text\":\"dead, or I shall have become a\"},{\"text\":\"different person, with a different face.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He continued to move to and fro over the soft carpet. In spite of the\"},{\"text\":\"bulkiness of his body there was a remarkable grace in his movements. It\"}]","[{\"text\":\"came out even in the gesture with which he thrust a hand into his pocket,\"},{\"text\":\"or manipulated a cigarette. More even than of strength, he gave an\"},{\"text\":\"impression of confidence and of an understanding tinged by irony. However\"}]","[{\"text\":\"nothing of the single-mindedness that\"},{\"text\":\"belongs to a fanatic. When he spoke of murder, suicide, venereal disease,\"},{\"text\":\"amputated limbs, and altered faces, it was with a faint air of persiflage.\"},{\"text\":\"'This is unavoidable,' his voice seemed to say; 'this is what we have got\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to do, unflinchingly. But this is not what we shall be doing when life is\"},{\"text\":\"worth living again.' A wave of admiration, almost of worship, flowed out\"},{\"text\":\"from Winston towards O'Brien. For the moment he had forgotten the shadowy\"}]","[{\"text\":\"at O'Brien's powerful shoulders and\"},{\"text\":\"his blunt-featured face, so ugly and yet so civilized, it was impossible\"},{\"text\":\"to believe that he could be defeated. There was no stratagem that he was\"},{\"text\":\"not equal to, no danger that he could not foresee. Even Julia seemed to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"be impressed. She had let her cigarette go out and was listening intently.\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien went on:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You will have heard rumours of the existence of the Brotherhood. No doubt\"},{\"text\":\"you have formed your own picture of it. You have imagined, probably, a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"huge underworld of conspirators, meeting secretly in cellars, scribbling\"},{\"text\":\"messages on walls, recognizing one another by codewords or by special\"},{\"text\":\"movements of the hand. Nothing of the kind exists. The members of the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"recognizing one another, and it is impossible\"},{\"text\":\"for any one member to be aware of the identity of more than a few others.\"},{\"text\":\"Goldstein himself, if he fell into the hands of the Thought Police, could\"}]","[{\"text\":\"information that would\"},{\"text\":\"lead them to a complete list. No such list exists. The Brotherhood cannot\"},{\"text\":\"be wiped out because it is not an organization in the ordinary sense.\"},{\"text\":\"Nothing holds it together except an idea which is indestructible. You\"}]","[{\"text\":\"will never have anything to sustain you, except the idea. You will get no\"},{\"text\":\"comradeship and no encouragement. When finally you are caught, you will\"},{\"text\":\"get no help. We never help our members. At most, when it is absolutely\"}]","[{\"text\":\"silenced, we are occasionally able to\"},{\"text\":\"smuggle a razor blade into a prisoner's cell. You will have to get used\"},{\"text\":\"to living without results and without hope. You will work for a while,\"},{\"text\":\"you will be caught, you will confess, and then you will die. Those are\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the only results that you will ever see. There is no possibility that any\"},{\"text\":\"perceptible change will happen within our own lifetime. We are the dead.\"},{\"text\":\"Our only true life is in the future. We shall take part in it as handfuls\"}]","[{\"text\":\"how far away that future may be, there\"},{\"text\":\"is no knowing. It might be a thousand years. At present nothing is possible\"},{\"text\":\"except to extend the area of sanity little by little. We cannot act\"}]","[{\"text\":\"from individual to\"},{\"text\":\"individual, generation after generation. In the face of the Thought Police\"},{\"text\":\"there is no other way.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He halted and looked for the third time at his wrist-watch.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"for you to leave, comrade,' he said to Julia. 'Wait.\"},{\"text\":\"The decanter is still half full.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He filled the glasses and raised his own glass by the stem.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"same faint\"},{\"text\":\"suggestion of irony. 'To the confusion of the Thought Police? To the\"},{\"text\":\"death of Big Brother? To humanity? To the future?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'To the past,' said Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"O'Brien gravely.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"They emptied their glasses, and a moment later Julia stood up to go.\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien took a small box from the top of a cabinet and handed her a flat\"},{\"text\":\"white tablet which he told her to place on her tongue. It was important,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"he said, not to go out smelling of wine: the lift attendants were very\"},{\"text\":\"observant. As soon as the door had shut behind her he appeared to forget\"},{\"text\":\"her existence. He took another pace or two up and down, then stopped.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to be settled,' he said. 'I assume that you have a\"},{\"text\":\"hiding-place of some kind?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston explained about the room over Mr Charrington's shop.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"something else for you.\"},{\"text\":\"It is important to change one's hiding-place frequently. Meanwhile I shall\"},{\"text\":\"send you a copy of THE BOOK'--even O'Brien, Winston noticed, seemed to\"},{\"text\":\"pronounce the words as though they were in italics--'Goldstein's book, you\"}]","[{\"text\":\"understand, as soon as possible. It may be some days before I can get hold\"},{\"text\":\"of one. There are not many in existence, as you can imagine. The Thought\"},{\"text\":\"Police hunt them down and destroy them almost as fast as we can produce\"}]","[{\"text\":\"difference. The book is indestructible. If\"},{\"text\":\"the last copy were gone, we could reproduce it almost word for word. Do\"},{\"text\":\"you carry a brief-case to work with you?' he added.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'As a rule, yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'What is it like?'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Black, very shabby. With two straps.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Black, two straps, very shabby--good. One day in the fairly near\"},{\"text\":\"future--I cannot give a date--one of the messages among your morning's\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and you will have to ask for a\"},{\"text\":\"repeat. On the following day you will go to work without your brief-case.\"},{\"text\":\"At some time during the day, in the street, a man will touch you on the\"},{\"text\":\"arm and say \\\"I think you have dropped your brief-case.\\\" The one he gives\"}]","[{\"text\":\"you will contain a copy of Goldstein's book. You will return it within\"},{\"text\":\"fourteen days.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"They were silent for a moment.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'There are a couple of minutes before you need go,' said O'Brien. 'We\"}]","[{\"text\":\"again--if we do meet again----'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston looked up at him. 'In the place where there is no darkness?'\"},{\"text\":\"he said hesitantly.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien nodded without appearance of surprise. 'In the place where there\"}]","[{\"text\":\"is no darkness,' he said, as though he had recognized the allusion. 'And\"},{\"text\":\"in the meantime, is there anything that you wish to say before you leave?\"},{\"text\":\"Any message? Any question?.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"question that he\"},{\"text\":\"wanted to ask: still less did he feel any impulse to utter high-sounding\"},{\"text\":\"generalities. Instead of anything directly connected with O'Brien or the\"},{\"text\":\"Brotherhood, there came into his mind a sort of composite picture of the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"his mother had spent her last days, and the little room\"},{\"text\":\"over Mr Charrington's shop, and the glass paperweight, and the steel\"},{\"text\":\"engraving in its rosewood frame. Almost at random he said:\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"rhyme that begins \\\"Oranges and lemons,\"},{\"text\":\"say the bells of St Clement's\\\"?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Again O'Brien nodded. With a sort of grave courtesy he completed the\"},{\"text\":\"stanza:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Oranges and lemons, say the bells of St Clement's,\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"You owe me three farthings, say the bells of St Martin's,\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"When will you pay me? say the bells of Old Bailey,\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"hen I grow rich, say the bells of Shoreditch.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You knew the last line!' said Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes, I knew the last line. And now, I am afraid, it is time for you to go.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"better let me give you one of these tablets.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"As Winston stood up O'Brien held out a hand. His powerful grip crushed\"},{\"text\":\"the bones of Winston's palm. At the door Winston looked back, but O'Brien\"}]","[{\"text\":\"putting him out of mind. He was waiting\"},{\"text\":\"with his hand on the switch that controlled the telescreen. Beyond him\"},{\"text\":\"Winston could see the writing-table with its green-shaded lamp and the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The incident was\"},{\"text\":\"closed. Within thirty seconds, it occurred to him, O'Brien would be back\"},{\"text\":\"at his interrupted and important work on behalf of the Party.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Chapter 9\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston was gelatinous with fatigue. Gelatinous was the right word. It had\"},{\"text\":\"come into his head spontaneously. His body seemed to have not only the\"},{\"text\":\"weakness of a jelly, but its translucency. He felt that if he held up his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"light through it. All the blood and\"},{\"text\":\"lymph had been drained out of him by an enormous debauch of work, leaving\"},{\"text\":\"only a frail structure of nerves, bones, and skin. All sensations seemed\"},{\"text\":\"to be magnified. His overalls fretted his shoulders, the pavement tickled\"}]","[{\"text\":\"his feet, even the opening and closing of a hand was an effort that made\"},{\"text\":\"his joints creak.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He had worked more than ninety hours in five days. So had everyone else in\"},{\"text\":\"the Ministry. Now it was