e enemy. Winston was taking part in a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"London squares at the moment when it\"},{\"text\":\"happened. It was night, and the white faces and the scarlet banners were\"},{\"text\":\"luridly floodlit. The square was packed with several thousand people,\"},{\"text\":\"including a block of about a thousand schoolchildren in the uniform of the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Spies. On a scarlet-draped platform an orator of the Inner Party, a small\"},{\"text\":\"lean man with disproportionately long arms and a large bald skull over\"},{\"text\":\"which a few lank locks straggled, was haranguing the crowd. A little\"}]","[{\"text\":\"with hatred, he gripped the neck of the\"},{\"text\":\"microphone with one hand while the other, enormous at the end of a bony\"},{\"text\":\"arm, clawed the air menacingly above his head. His voice, made metallic by\"}]","[{\"text\":\"atrocities, massacres,\"},{\"text\":\"deportations, lootings, rapings, torture of prisoners, bombing of\"},{\"text\":\"civilians, lying propaganda, unjust aggressions, broken treaties. It was\"},{\"text\":\"almost impossible to listen to him without being first convinced and then\"}]","[{\"text\":\"maddened. At every few moments the fury of the crowd boiled over and the\"},{\"text\":\"voice of the speaker was drowned by a wild beast-like roaring that rose\"},{\"text\":\"uncontrollably from thousands of throats. The most savage yells of all\"}]","[{\"text\":\"speech had been proceeding for perhaps\"},{\"text\":\"twenty minutes when a messenger hurried on to the platform and a scrap of\"},{\"text\":\"paper was slipped into the speaker's hand. He unrolled and read it without\"}]","[{\"text\":\"manner, or in the\"},{\"text\":\"content of what he was saying, but suddenly the names were different.\"},{\"text\":\"Without words said, a wave of understanding rippled through the crowd.\"},{\"text\":\"Oceania was at war with Eastasia! The next moment there was a tremendous\"}]","[{\"text\":\"banners and posters with which the square was decorated\"},{\"text\":\"were all wrong! Quite half of them had the wrong faces on them. It was\"},{\"text\":\"sabotage! The agents of Goldstein had been at work! There was a riotous\"}]","[{\"text\":\"banners torn to shreds\"},{\"text\":\"and trampled underfoot. The Spies performed prodigies of activity in\"},{\"text\":\"clambering over the rooftops and cutting the streamers that fluttered from\"},{\"text\":\"the chimneys. But within two or three minutes it was all over. The orator,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"still gripping the neck of the microphone, his shoulders hunched forward,\"},{\"text\":\"his free hand clawing at the air, had gone straight on with his speech.\"},{\"text\":\"One minute more, and the feral roars of rage were again bursting from the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"before, except that the target had\"},{\"text\":\"been changed.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The thing that impressed Winston in looking back was that the speaker had\"},{\"text\":\"switched from one line to the other actually in midsentence, not only\"}]","[{\"text\":\"breaking the syntax. But at the moment\"},{\"text\":\"he had other things to preoccupy him. It was during the moment of disorder\"},{\"text\":\"while the posters were being torn down that a man whose face he did not\"}]","[{\"text\":\"I think you've\"},{\"text\":\"dropped your brief-case.' He took the brief-case abstractedly, without\"},{\"text\":\"speaking. He knew that it would be days before he had an opportunity to\"},{\"text\":\"look inside it. The instant that the demonstration was over he went\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Ministry of Truth, though the time was now nearly\"},{\"text\":\"twenty-three hours. The entire staff of the Ministry had done likewise.\"},{\"text\":\"The orders already issuing from the telescreen, recalling them to their\"},{\"text\":\"posts, were hardly necessary.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Oceania was at war with Eastasia: Oceania had always been at war with\"},{\"text\":\"Eastasia. A large part of the political literature of five years was now\"},{\"text\":\"completely obsolete. Reports and records of all kinds, newspapers, books,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"photographs--all had to be rectified at\"},{\"text\":\"lightning speed. Although no directive was ever issued, it was known that\"},{\"text\":\"the chiefs of the Department intended that within one week no reference\"}]","[{\"text\":\"should remain in\"},{\"text\":\"existence anywhere. The work was overwhelming, all the more so because\"},{\"text\":\"the processes that it involved could not be called by their true\"},{\"text\":\"names. Everyone in the Records Department worked eighteen hours in the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"two three-hour snatches of sleep. Mattresses were brought\"},{\"text\":\"up from the cellars and pitched all over the corridors: meals consisted of\"},{\"text\":\"sandwiches and Victory Coffee wheeled round on trolleys by attendants from\"}]","[{\"text\":\"broke off for one of his spells of\"},{\"text\":\"sleep he tried to leave his desk clear of work, and each time that he\"},{\"text\":\"crawled back sticky-eyed and aching, it was to find that another shower\"},{\"text\":\"of paper cylinders had covered the desk like a snowdrift, half-burying the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"speakwrite and overflowing on to the floor, so that the first job was\"},{\"text\":\"always to stack them into a neat enough pile to give him room to work.\"},{\"text\":\"What was worst of all was that the work was by no means purely mechanical.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"substitute one name for another, but any\"},{\"text\":\"detailed report of events demanded care and imagination. Even the\"},{\"text\":\"geographical knowledge that one needed in transferring the war from one\"},{\"text\":\"part of the world to another was considerable.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"By the third day his eyes ached unbearably and his spectacles needed wiping\"},{\"text\":\"every few minutes. It was like struggling with some crushing physical task,\"},{\"text\":\"something which one had the right to refuse and which one was nevertheless\"}]","[{\"text\":\"In so far as he had time to remember\"},{\"text\":\"it, he was not troubled by the fact that every word he murmured into the\"},{\"text\":\"speakwrite, every stroke of his ink-pencil, was a deliberate lie. He was\"},{\"text\":\"as anxious as anyone else in the Department that the forgery should be\"}]","[{\"text\":\"perfect. On the morning of the sixth day the dribble of cylinders slowed\"},{\"text\":\"down. For as much as half an hour nothing came out of the tube; then one\"},{\"text\":\"more cylinder, then nothing. Everywhere at about the same time the work\"}]","[{\"text\":\"secret sigh went through the\"},{\"text\":\"Department. A mighty deed, which could never be mentioned, had been\"},{\"text\":\"achieved. It was now impossible for any human being to prove by documentary\"},{\"text\":\"evidence that the war with Eurasia had ever happened. At twelve hundred it\"}]","[{\"text\":\"was unexpectedly announced that all workers in the Ministry were free till\"},{\"text\":\"tomorrow morning. Winston, still carrying the brief-case containing the\"},{\"text\":\"book, which had remained between his feet while he worked and under his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"shaved himself, and almost fell asleep in\"},{\"text\":\"his bath, although the water was barely more than tepid.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"With a sort of voluptuous creaking in his joints he climbed the stair above\"}]","[{\"text\":\"longer. He opened\"},{\"text\":\"the window, lit the dirty little oilstove and put on a pan of water for\"},{\"text\":\"coffee. Julia would arrive presently: meanwhile there was the book. He\"},{\"text\":\"sat down in the sluttish armchair and undid the straps of the brief-case.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"A heavy black volume, amateurishly bound, with no name or title on the\"},{\"text\":\"cover. The print also looked slightly irregular. The pages were worn at\"},{\"text\":\"the edges, and fell apart, easily, as though the book had passed through\"}]","[{\"text\":\"title-page ran:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"THE THEORY AND PRACTICE OF\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"OLIGARCHICAL COLLECTIVISM\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"by\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"mmanuel Goldstein\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston began reading:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Chapter I\"},{\"text\":\"Ignorance is Strength\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the Neolithic Age,\"},{\"text\":\"there have been three kinds of people in the world, the High, the Middle,\"},{\"text\":\"and the Low. They have been subdivided in many ways, they have borne\"},{\"text\":\"countless different names, and their relative numbers, as well as their\"}]","[{\"text\":\"one another, have varied from age to age: but the\"},{\"text\":\"essential structure of society has never altered. Even after enormous\"},{\"text\":\"upheavals and seemingly irrevocable changes, the same pattern has always\"}]","[{\"text\":\"return to equilibrium,\"},{\"text\":\"however far it is pushed one way or the other.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The aims of these groups are entirely irreconcilable...\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the fact that he\"},{\"text\":\"was reading, in comfort and safety. He was alone: no telescreen, no ear at\"},{\"text\":\"the keyhole, no nervous impulse to glance over his shoulder or cover the\"},{\"text\":\"page with his hand. The sweet summer air played against his cheek. From\"}]","[{\"text\":\"there floated the faint shouts of children: in the room\"},{\"text\":\"itself there was no sound except the insect voice of the clock. He settled\"},{\"text\":\"deeper into the arm-chair and put his feet up on the fender. It was bliss,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"book of which one\"},{\"text\":\"knows that one will ultimately read and re-read every word, he opened it\"},{\"text\":\"at a different place and found himself at Chapter III. He went on reading:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Chapter III\"},{\"text\":\"War is Peace\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The splitting up of the world into three great super-states was an event\"},{\"text\":\"which could be and indeed was foreseen before the middle of the twentieth\"},{\"text\":\"century. With the absorption of Europe by Russia and of the British Empire\"}]","[{\"text\":\"three existing powers, Eurasia and\"},{\"text\":\"Oceania, were already effectively in being. The third, Eastasia, only\"},{\"text\":\"emerged as a distinct unit after another decade of confused fighting. The\"},{\"text\":\"frontiers between the three super-states are in some places arbitrary, and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"in others they fluctuate according to the fortunes of war, but in general\"},{\"text\":\"they follow geographical lines. Eurasia comprises the whole of the northern\"},{\"text\":\"part of the European and Asiatic land-mass, from Portugal to the Bering\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Americas, the Atlantic islands including the\"},{\"text\":\"British Isles, Australasia, and the southern portion of Africa. Eastasia,\"},{\"text\":\"smaller than the others and with a less definite western frontier,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the Japanese islands\"},{\"text\":\"and a large but fluctuating portion of Manchuria, Mongolia, and Tibet.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"In one combination or another, these three super-states are permanently at\"}]","[{\"text\":\"War, however, is no\"},{\"text\":\"longer the desperate, annihilating struggle that it was in the early\"},{\"text\":\"decades of the twentieth century. It is a warfare of limited aims between\"},{\"text\":\"combatants who are unable to destroy one another, have no material cause\"}]","[{\"text\":\"for fighting and are not divided by any genuine ideological difference.\"},{\"text\":\"This is not to say that either the conduct of war, or the prevailing\"},{\"t