ulia, are you awake?' said Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes, my love, I'm listening. Go on. It's marvellous.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He continued reading:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"irreconcilable. The aim of\"},{\"text\":\"the High is to remain where they are. The aim of the Middle is to change\"},{\"text\":\"places with the High. The aim of the Low, when they have an aim--for it\"},{\"text\":\"is an abiding characteristic of the Low that they are too much crushed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"by drudgery to be more than intermittently conscious of anything outside\"},{\"text\":\"their daily lives--is to abolish all distinctions and create a society in\"},{\"text\":\"which all men shall be equal. Thus throughout history a struggle which is\"}]","[{\"text\":\"over and over again. For long periods\"},{\"text\":\"the High seem to be securely in power, but sooner or later there always\"},{\"text\":\"comes a moment when they lose either their belief in themselves or their\"},{\"text\":\"capacity to govern efficiently, or both. They are then overthrown by the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Middle, who enlist the Low on their side by pretending to them that they\"},{\"text\":\"are fighting for liberty and justice. As soon as they have reached their\"},{\"text\":\"objective, the Middle thrust the Low back into their old position of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"High. Presently a new Middle group\"},{\"text\":\"splits off from one of the other groups, or from both of them, and the\"},{\"text\":\"struggle begins over again. Of the three groups, only the Low are never\"},{\"text\":\"even temporarily successful in achieving their aims. It would be an\"}]","[{\"text\":\"exaggeration to say that throughout history there has been no progress of\"},{\"text\":\"a material kind. Even today, in a period of decline, the average human\"},{\"text\":\"being is physically better off than he was a few centuries ago. But no\"}]","[{\"text\":\"manners, no reform or revolution has\"