ablishing liberty and equality was more and more openly\"},{\"text\":\"abandoned. The new movements which appeared in the middle years of the\"},{\"text\":\"century, Ingsoc in Oceania, Neo-Bolshevism in Eurasia, Death-Worship, as\"}]","[{\"text\":\"had the conscious aim of perpetuating\"},{\"text\":\"UNfreedom and INequality. These new movements, of course, grew out of the\"},{\"text\":\"old ones and tended to keep their names and pay lip-service to their\"},{\"text\":\"ideology. But the purpose of all of them was to arrest progress and freeze\"}]","[{\"text\":\"history at a chosen moment. The familiar pendulum swing was to happen once\"},{\"text\":\"more, and then stop. As usual, the High were to be turned out by the\"},{\"text\":\"Middle, who would then become the High; but this time, by conscious\"}]","[{\"text\":\"maintain their position permanently.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The new doctrines arose partly because of the accumulation of historical\"},{\"text\":\"knowledge, and the growth of the historical sense, which had hardly existed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"history was now\"},{\"text\":\"intelligible, or appeared to be so; and if it was intelligible, then it\"},{\"text\":\"was alterable. But the principal, underlying cause was that, as early\"},{\"text\":\"as the beginning of the twentieth century, human equality had become\"}]","[{\"text\":\"possible. It was still true that men were not equal in their\"},{\"text\":\"native talents and that functions had to be specialized in ways that\"},{\"text\":\"favoured some individuals against others; but there was no longer any real\"}]","[{\"text\":\"large differences of wealth. In earlier\"},{\"text\":\"ages, class distinctions had been not only inevitable but desirable.\"},{\"text\":\"Inequality was the price of civilization. With the development of machine\"}]","[{\"text\":\"was still necessary\"},{\"text\":\"for human beings to do different kinds of work, it was no longer necessary\"},{\"text\":\"for them to live 