e does is indifferent. His friendships, his\"},{\"text\":\"relaxations, his behaviour towards his wife and children, the expression\"}]","[{\"text\":\"words he mutters in sleep, even the\"},{\"text\":\"characteristic movements of his body, are all jealously scrutinized. Not\"},{\"text\":\"only any actual misdemeanour, but any eccentricity, however small, any\"},{\"text\":\"change of habits, any nervous mannerism that could possibly be the symptom\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of an inner struggle, is certain to be detected. He has no freedom of\"},{\"text\":\"choice in any direction whatever. On the other hand his actions are not\"},{\"text\":\"regulated by law or by any clearly formulated code of behaviour. In Oceania\"}]","[{\"text\":\"which, when detected, mean certain\"},{\"text\":\"death are not formally forbidden, and the endless purges, arrests,\"},{\"text\":\"tortures, imprisonments, and vaporizations are not inflicted as punishment\"},{\"text\":\"for crimes which have actually been committed, but are merely the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"wiping-out of persons who might perhaps commit a crime at some time in the\"},{\"text\":\"future. A Party member is required to have not only the right opinions,\"},{\"text\":\"but the right instincts. Many of the beliefs and attitudes demanded of him\"}]","[{\"text\":\"not be stated without laying bare the\"},{\"text\":\"contradictions inherent in Ingsoc. If he is a person naturally orthodox\"},{\"text\":\"(in Newspeak a GOODTHINKER), he will in all circumstances know, without\"},{\"text\":\"taking thought, what is the true belief or the desirable emotion. But in\"}]","[{\"text\":\"any case an elaborate mental training, undergone in childhood and grouping\"},{\"text\":\"itself round the Newspeak words CRIMESTOP, BLACKWHITE, and DOUBLETHINK,\"},{\"text\":\"makes him unwilling and unable to think too deeply on any subject whatever.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"expected to have no private emotions and no respites\"},{\"text\":\"from enthusiasm. He is supposed to live in a continuous frenzy of hatred\"},{\"text\":\"of foreign enemies and internal traitors, triumph over victories, and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The discontents\"},{\"text\":\"produced by his bare, unsatisfying life are deliberately turned outwards\"},{\"text\":\"and dissipated by such devices as the Two Minutes Hate, and the\"},{\"text\":\"speculations which might possibly induce a sceptical or rebellious attitude\"}]","[{\"text\":\"advance by his early acquired inner discipline. The first\"},{\"text\":\"and simplest stage in the discipline, which can be taught even to young\"},{\"text\":\"children, is called, in Newspeak, CRIMESTOP. CRIMESTOP means the faculty\"}]","[{\"text\":\"instinct, at the threshold of any dangerous\"},{\"text\":\"thought. It includes the power of not grasping analogies, of failing to\"},{\"text\":\"perceive logical errors, of misunderstanding the simplest arguments if\"}]","[{\"text\":\"repelled by any train\"},{\"text\":\"of thought which is capable of leading in a heretical direction. CRIMESTOP,\"},{\"text\":\"in short, means protective stupidity. But stupidity is not enough. On the\"},{\"text\":\"contrary, orthodoxy in the full sense demands a control over one's own\"}]","[{\"text\":\"mental processes as complete as that of a contortionist over his body.\"},{\"text\":\"Oceanic society rests ultimately on the belief that Big Brother is\"},{\"text\":\"omnipotent and that the Party is infallible. But since in reality Big\"}]","[{\"text\":\"party is not infallible, there is need\"},{\"text\":\"for an unwearying, moment-to-moment flexibility in the treatment of facts.\"},{\"text\":\"The keyword here is BLACKWHITE. Like so many Newspeak words, this word has\"}]","[{\"text\":\"opponent, it means the\"},{\"text\":\"habit of impudently claiming that black is white, in contradiction of the\"},{\"text\":\"plain facts. Applied to a Party member, it means a loyal willingness to\"},{\"text\":\"say that black is white when Party discipline demands this. But it means\"}]","[{\"text\":\"also the ability to BELIEVE that black is white, and more, to KNOW that\"},{\"text\":\"black is white, and to forget that one has ever believed the contrary.\"},{\"text\":\"This demands a continuous alteration of the past, made possible by the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"embraces all the rest, and which is known\"},{\"text\":\"in Newspeak as DOUBLETHINK.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The alteration of the past is necessary for two reasons, one of which is\"},{\"text\":\"subsidiary and, so to speak, precautionary. The subsidiary reason is that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the Party member, like the proletarian, tolerates present-day conditions\"},{\"text\":\"partly because he has no standards of comparison. He must be cut off from\"},{\"text\":\"the past, just as he must be cut off from foreign countries, because it is\"}]","[{\"text\":\"is better off than his ancestors and\"},{\"text\":\"that the average level of material comfort is constantly rising. But by\"},{\"text\":\"far the more important reason for the readjustment of the past is the\"},{\"text\":\"need to safeguard the infallibility of the Party. It is not merely that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"speeches, statistics, and records of every kind must be constantly brought\"},{\"text\":\"up to date in order to show that the predictions of the Party were in\"},{\"text\":\"all cases right. It is also that no change in doctrine or in political\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to change one's mind, or even one's\"},{\"text\":\"policy, is a confession of weakness. If, for example, Eurasia or Eastasia\"},{\"text\":\"(whichever it may be) is the enemy today, then that country must always\"},{\"text\":\"have been the enemy. And if the facts say otherwise then the facts must\"}]","[{\"text\":\"be altered. Thus history is continuously rewritten. This day-to-day\"},{\"text\":\"falsification of the past, carried out by the Ministry of Truth, is as\"},{\"text\":\"necessary to the stability of the regime as the work of repression and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of Love.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The mutability of the past is the central tenet of Ingsoc. Past events,\"},{\"text\":\"it is argued, have no objective existence, but survive only in written\"},{\"text\":\"records and in human memories. The past is whatever the records and the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"memories agree upon. And since the Party is in full control of all records\"},{\"text\":\"and in equally full control of the minds of its members, it follows that\"},{\"text\":\"the past is whatever the Party chooses to make it. It also follows that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"never has been altered in any specific\"},{\"text\":\"instance. For when it has been recreated in whatever shape is needed at\"},{\"text\":\"the moment, then this new version IS the past, and no different past can\"}]","[{\"text\":\"happens, the same\"},{\"text\":\"event has to be altered out of recognition several times in the course of\"},{\"text\":\"a year. At all times the Party is in possession of absolute truth, and\"},{\"text\":\"clearly the absolute can never have been different from what it is now.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that the control of the past depends above all on the\"},{\"text\":\"training of memory. To make sure that all written records agree with\"},{\"text\":\"the orthodoxy of the moment is merely a mechanical act. But it is also\"}]","[{\"text\":\"desired manner. And if\"},{\"text\":\"it is necessary to rearrange one's memories or to tamper with written\"},{\"text\":\"records, then it is necessary to FORGET that one has done so. The trick of\"},{\"text\":\"doing this can be learned like any other mental technique. It is learned\"}]","[{\"text\":\"by the majority of Party members, and certainly by all who are intelligent\"},{\"text\":\"as well as orthodox. In Oldspeak it is called, quite frankly, 'reality\"},{\"text\":\"control'. In Newspeak it is called DOUBLETHINK, though DOUBLETHINK\"},{\"text\":\"comprises much else as well.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"DOUBLETHINK means the power of holding two contradictory beliefs in one's\"},{\"text\":\"mind simultaneously, and accepting both of them. The Party intellectual\"},{\"text\":\"knows in which direction his memories must be altered; he therefore knows\"}]","[{\"text\":\"reality; but by the exercise of DOUBLETHINK\"},{\"text\":\"he also satisfies himself that reality is not violated. The process has to\"},{\"text\":\"be conscious, or it would not be carried out with sufficient precision,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"with it a feeling of\"},{\"text\":\"falsity and hence of guilt. DOUBLETHINK lies at the very heart of Ingsoc,\"},{\"text\":\"since the essential act of the Party is to use conscious deception while\"},{\"text\":\"retaining the firmness of purpose that goes with complete honesty. To tell\"}]","[{\"text\":\"deliberate lies while genuinely believing in them, to forget any fact that\"},{\"text\":\"has become inconvenient, and then, when it becomes necessary again, to\"},{\"text\":\"draw it back from oblivion for just so long as it is needed, to deny the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"all the while to take account of the\"},{\"text\":\"reality which one denies--all this is indispensably necessary. Even in\"},{\"text\":\"using the word DOUBLETHINK it is necessary to exercise DOUBLETHINK. For\"},{\"text\":\"by using the word one admits that one is tampering with reality; by a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"fresh act of DOUBLETHINK one erases this knowledge; and so on indefinitely,\"},{\"text\":\"with the lie always one leap ahead of the truth. Ultimately it is by means\"},{\"text\":\"of DOUBLETHINK that the Party has been able--and may, for all we know,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"years--to arrest the course of\"},{\"text\":\"history.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"All past oligarchies have fallen from power either because they ossified\"},{\"text\":\"or because they grew soft. Either they became stupid and arrogant, failed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"circumstances, and were overthrown; or\"},{\"text\":\"they became liberal and cowardly, made concessions when they should have\"},{\"text\":\"used force, and once again were overthrown. They fell, that is to say,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"It is the\"},{\"text\":\"achievement of the Party to have produced a system of thought in which\"},{\"text\":\"both conditions can exist simultaneously. And upon no other intellectual\"},{\"text\":\"basis could the dominion of the Party be made permanent. If one is to rule,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ruling, one must be able to dislocate the sense of reality.\"},{\"text\":\"For the secret of rulership is to combine a belief in one's own\"},{\"text\":\"infallibility with the Power to learn from past mistakes.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"said that the subtlest practitioners of DOUBLETHINK are\"},{\"text\":\"those who invented DOUBLETHINK and know that it is a vast system of mental\"},{\"text\":\"cheating. In our society, those who have the best knowledge of what is\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the world as it is.\"},{\"text\":\"In general, the greater the understanding, the greater the delusion; the\"},{\"text\":\"more intelligent, the less sane. One clear illustration of this is the\"},{\"text\":\"fact that war hysteria increases in intensity as one rises in the social\"}]","[{\"text\":\"scale. Those whose attitude towards the war is most nearly rational are\"},{\"text\":\"the subject peoples of the disputed territories. To these people the war\"},{\"text\":\"is simply a continuous calamity which sweeps to and fro over their bodies\"}]","[{\"text\":\"winning is a matter of complete\"},{\"text\":\"indifference to them. They are aware that a change of overlordship means\"},{\"text\":\"simply that they will be doing the same work as before for new masters who\"},{\"text\":\"treat them in the same manner as the old ones. The slightly more favoured\"}]","[{\"text\":\"workers whom we call 'the proles' are only intermittently conscious of the\"},{\"text\":\"war. When it is necessary they can be prodded into frenzies of fear and\"},{\"text\":\"hatred, but when left to themselves they are capable of forgetting for\"}]","[{\"text\":\"happening. It is in the ranks of the Party,\"},{\"text\":\"and above all of the Inner Party, that the true war enthusiasm is found.\"},{\"text\":\"World-conquest is believed in most firmly by those who know it to be\"}]","[{\"text\":\"opposites--knowledge with\"},{\"text\":\"ignorance, cynicism with fanaticism--is one of the chief distinguishing\"},{\"text\":\"marks of Oceanic society. The official ideology abounds with contradictions\"},{\"text\":\"even when there is no practical reason for them. Thus, the Party rejects\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and vilifies every principle for which the Socialist movement originally\"},{\"text\":\"stood, and it chooses to do this in the name of Socialism. It preaches\"},{\"text\":\"a contempt for the working class unexampled for centuries past, and it\"}]","[{\"text\":\"which was at one time peculiar to manual\"},{\"text\":\"workers and was adopted for that reason. It systematically undermines the\"},{\"text\":\"solidarity of the family, and it calls its leader by a name which is a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the names of the\"},{\"text\":\"four Ministries by which we are governed exhibit a sort of impudence in\"},{\"text\":\"their deliberate reversal of the facts. The Ministry of Peace concerns\"},{\"text\":\"itself with war, the Ministry of Truth with lies, the Ministry of Love\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the Ministry of Plenty with starvation. These\"},{\"text\":\"contradictions are not accidental, nor do they result from ordinary\"},{\"text\":\"hypocrisy; they are deliberate exercises in DOUBLETHINK. For it is only\"}]","[{\"text\":\"indefinitely.\"},{\"text\":\"In no other way could the ancient cycle be broken. If human equality is\"},{\"text\":\"to be for ever averted--if the High, as we have called them, are to keep\"},{\"text\":\"their places permanently--then the prevailing mental condition must be\"}]","[{\"text\":\"insanity.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"But there is one question which until this moment we have almost ignored.\"},{\"text\":\"It is; WHY should human equality be averted? Supposing that the mechanics\"},{\"text\":\"of the process have been rightly described, what is the motive for this\"}]","[{\"text\":\"huge, accurately planned effort to freeze history at a particular moment\"},{\"text\":\"of time?\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Here we reach the central secret. As we have seen. the mystique of the\"},{\"text\":\"Party, and above all of the Inner Party, depends upon DOUBLETHINK But\"}]","[{\"text\":\"deeper than this lies the original motive, the never-questioned instinct\"},{\"text\":\"that first led to the seizure of power and brought DOUBLETHINK, the\"},{\"text\":\"Thought Police, continuous warfare, and all the other necessary\"}]","[{\"text\":\"afterwards. This motive really consists...\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston became aware of silence, as one becomes aware of a new sound. It\"},{\"text\":\"seemed to him that Julia had been very still for some time past. She was\"}]","[{\"text\":\"naked from the waist upwards, with her cheek pillowed\"},{\"text\":\"on her hand and one dark lock tumbling across her eyes. Her breast rose\"},{\"text\":\"and fell slowly and regularly.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Julia.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"No answer.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Julia, are you awake?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"No answer. She was asleep. He shut the book, put it carefully on the floor,\"},{\"text\":\"lay down, and pulled the coverlet over both of them.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"secret. He understood\"},{\"text\":\"HOW; he did not understand WHY. Chapter I, like Chapter III, had not\"},{\"text\":\"actually told him anything that he did not know, it had merely systematized\"},{\"text\":\"the knowledge that he possessed already. But after reading it he knew\"}]","[{\"text\":\"better than before that he was not mad. Being in a minority, even a\"},{\"text\":\"minority of one, did not make you mad. There was truth and there was\"},{\"text\":\"untruth, and if you clung to the truth even against the whole world, you\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sinking sun slanted in through the\"},{\"text\":\"window and fell across the pillow. He shut his eyes. The sun on his face\"},{\"text\":\"and the girl's smooth body touching his own gave him a strong, sleepy,\"},{\"text\":\"confident feeling. He was safe, everything was all right. He fell asleep\"}]","[{\"text\":\"murmuring 'Sanity is not statistical,' with the feeling that this remark\"},{\"text\":\"contained in it a profound wisdom.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"*****\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"When he woke it was with the sensation of having slept for a long time,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the old-fashioned clock told him that it was only\"},{\"text\":\"twenty-thirty. He lay dozing for a while; then the usual deep-lunged\"},{\"text\":\"singing struck up from the yard below:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'It was only an 'opeless fancy,\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"It passed like an Ipril dye,\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"But a look an' a word an' the dreams they stirred\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"hey 'ave stolen my 'eart awye!'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The drivelling song seemed to have kept its popularity. You still heard it\"},{\"text\":\"all over the place. It had outlived the Hate Song. Julia woke at the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and got out of bed.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I'm hungry,' she said. 'Let's make some more coffee. Damn! The stove's\"},{\"text\":\"gone out and the water's cold.' She picked the stove up and shook it.\"},{\"text\":\"'There's no oil in it.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'We can get some from old Charrington, I expect.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'The funny thing is I made sure it was full. I'm going to put my clothes\"},{\"text\":\"on,' she added. 'It seems to have got colder.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"himself. The indefatigable voice sang on:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'They sye that time 'eals all things,\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"They sye you can always forget;\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"But the smiles an' the tears acrorss the years\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"hey twist my 'eart-strings yet!'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"As he fastened the belt of his overalls he strolled across to the window.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The sun must have gone down behind the houses; it was not shining into the\"},{\"text\":\"yard any longer. The flagstones were wet as though they had just been\"},{\"text\":\"washed, and he had the feeling that the sky had been washed too, so fresh\"}]","[{\"text\":\"chimney-pots. Tirelessly the woman\"},{\"text\":\"marched to and fro, corking and uncorking herself, singing and falling\"},{\"text\":\"silent, and pegging out more diapers, and more and yet more. He wondered\"},{\"text\":\"whether she took in washing for a living or was merely the slave of twenty\"}]","[{\"text\":\"or thirty grandchildren. Julia had come across to his side; together they\"},{\"text\":\"gazed down with a sort of fascination at the sturdy figure below. As he\"},{\"text\":\"looked at the woman in her characteristic attitude, her thick arms reaching\"}]","[{\"text\":\"mare-like buttocks protruded, it struck him\"},{\"text\":\"for the first time that she was beautiful. It had never before occurred to\"},{\"text\":\"him that the body of a woman of fifty, blown up to monstrous dimensions by\"}]","[{\"text\":\"was coarse in the\"},{\"text\":\"grain like an over-ripe turnip, could be beautiful. But it was so, and\"},{\"text\":\"after all, he thought, why not? The solid, contourless body, like a block\"},{\"text\":\"of granite, and the rasping red skin, bore the same relation to the body\"}]","[{\"text\":\"rose-hip to the rose. Why should the fruit be held\"},{\"text\":\"inferior to the flower?\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'She's beautiful,' he murmured.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'She's a metre across the hips, easily,' said Julia.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of beauty,' said Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He held Julia's supple waist easily encircled by his arm. From the hip to\"},{\"text\":\"the knee her flank was against his. Out of their bodies no child would\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Only by word of\"},{\"text\":\"mouth, from mind to mind, could they pass on the secret. The woman down\"},{\"text\":\"there had no mind, she had only strong arms, a warm heart, and a fertile\"},{\"text\":\"belly. He wondered how many children she had given birth to. It might\"}]","[{\"text\":\"She had had her momentary flowering, a year, perhaps,\"},{\"text\":\"of wild-rose beauty and then she had suddenly swollen like a fertilized\"},{\"text\":\"fruit and grown hard and red and coarse, and then her life had been\"}]","[{\"text\":\"polishing, mending,\"},{\"text\":\"scrubbing, laundering, first for children, then for grandchildren, over\"},{\"text\":\"thirty unbroken years. At the end of it she was still singing. The mystical\"},{\"text\":\"reverence that he felt for her was somehow mixed up with the aspect of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the pale, cloudless sky, stretching away behind the chimney-pots into\"},{\"text\":\"interminable distance. It was curious to think that the sky was the same\"},{\"text\":\"for everybody, in Eurasia or Eastasia as well as here. And the people\"}]","[{\"text\":\"same--everywhere, all over the world,\"},{\"text\":\"hundreds of thousands of millions of people just like this, people ignorant\"},{\"text\":\"of one another's existence, held apart by walls of hatred and lies, and\"},{\"text\":\"yet almost exactly the same--peopl