. He confessed to the assassination of eminent Party\"},{\"text\":\"members, the distribution of seditious pamphlets, embezzlement of public\"},{\"text\":\"funds, sale of military secrets, sabotage of every kind. He confessed that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"as far back as\"},{\"text\":\"1968. He confessed that he was a religious believer, an admirer of\"},{\"text\":\"capitalism, and a sexual pervert. He confessed that he had murdered his\"},{\"text\":\"wife, although he knew, and his questioners must have known, that his wife\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He confessed that for years he had been in personal touch\"},{\"text\":\"with Goldstein and had been a member of an underground organization which\"},{\"text\":\"had included almost every human being he had ever known. It was easier to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"everybody. Besides, in a sense it was all\"},{\"text\":\"true. It was true that he had been the enemy of the Party, and in the eyes\"},{\"text\":\"of the Party there was no distinction between the thought and the deed.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"kind. They stood out in his mind\"},{\"text\":\"disconnectedly, like pictures with blackness all round them.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He was in a cell which might have been either dark or light, because he\"}]","[{\"text\":\"some kind of\"},{\"text\":\"instrument was ticking slowly and regularly. The eyes grew larger and more\"},{\"text\":\"luminous. Suddenly he floated out of his seat, dived into the eyes, and\"},{\"text\":\"was swallowed up.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"dazzling lights.\"},{\"text\":\"A man in a white coat was reading the dials. There was a tramp of heavy\"},{\"text\":\"boots outside. The door clanged open. The waxed-faced officer marched in,\"},{\"text\":\"followed by two guards.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Room 101,' said the officer.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The man in the white coat did not turn round. He did not look at Winston\"},{\"text\":\"either; he was looking only at the dials.\"},{\"text\":\"\"