\"so much as to be understood. O'Brien\"},{\"text\":\"had tortured him to the edge of lunacy, and in a little while, it was\"},{\"text\":\"certain, he would send him to his death. It made no difference. In some\"},{\"text\":\"sense that went deeper than friendship, they were intimates: somewhere or\"}]","[{\"text\":\"other, although the actual words might never be spoken, there was a place\"},{\"text\":\"where they could meet and talk. O'Brien was looking down at him with an\"},{\"text\":\"expression which suggested that the same thought might be in his own mind.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"conversational tone.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Do you know where you are, Winston?' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I don't know. I can guess. In the Ministry of Love.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Do you know how long you have been here?'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'I don't know. Days, weeks, months--I think it is months.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'And why do you imagine that we bring people to this place?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'To make them confess.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the reason. Try again.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'To punish them.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No!' exclaimed O'Brien. His voice had changed extraordinarily, and his\"},{\"text\":\"face had suddenly become both stern and animated. 'No! Not merely to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"confession, not to punish you. Shall I tell you why we have\"},{\"text\":\"brought you here? To cure you! To make you sane! Will you understand,\"},{\"text\":\"Winston, that no one whom we bring to this place ever leaves our hands\"}]","[{\"text\":\"those stupid crimes that you have\"},{\"text\":\"committed. The Party is not interested in the overt act: the thought is\"},{\"text\":\"all we care about. We do not merely destroy our enemies, we change them.\"},{\"text\":\"Do you understand what I mean by that?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He was bending over Winston. His face looked enormous because of its\"},{\"text\":\"nearness, and hideously ugly because it was seen from below. Moreover it\"},{\"text\":\"was filled with a sort of exaltation, a lunatic intensity. Again Winston's\"}]","[{\"text\":\"he would have cowered deeper into\"},{\"text\":\"the bed. He felt certain that O'Brien was about to twist the dial out of\"},{\"text\":\"sheer wantonness. At this moment, however, O'Brien turned away. He took a\"},{\"text\":\"pace or two up and down. Then he continued less vehemently:\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'The first thing for you to understand is that in this place there are no\"},{\"text\":\"martyrdoms. You have read of the religious persecutions of the past. In\"},{\"text\":\"the Middle Ages there was the Inquisition. It was a failure. It set out\"}]","[{\"text\":\"perpetuating it. For every heretic it\"},{\"text\":\"burned at the stake, thousands of others rose up. Why was that? Because\"},{\"text\":\"the Inquisition killed its enemies in the open, and killed them while\"},{\"text\":\"they were still unrepentant: in fact, it killed them because they were\"}]","[{\"text\":\"unrepentant. Men were dying because they would not abandon their true\"},{\"text\":\"beliefs. Naturally all the glory belonged to the victim and all the shame\"},{\"text\":\"to the Inquisitor who burned him. Later, in the twentieth century, there\"}]","[{\"text\":\"called. There were the German Nazis\"},{\"text\":\"and the Russian Communists. The Russians persecuted heresy more cruelly\"},{\"text\":\"than the Inquisition had done. And they imagined that they had learned\"},{\"text\":\"from the mistakes of the past; they knew, at any rate, that one must not\"}]","[{\"text\":\"make martyrs. Before they exposed their victims to public trial, they\"},{\"text\":\"deliberately set themselves to destroy their dignity. They wore them down\"},{\"text\":\"by torture and solitude until they were despicable, cringing wretches,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"their mouths, covering themselves with\"},{\"text\":\"abuse, accusing and sheltering behind one another, whimpering for mercy.\"},{\"text\":\"And yet after only a few years the same thing had happened over again.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"was forgotten. Once\"},{\"text\":\"again, why was it? In the first place, because the confessions that they\"},{\"text\":\"had made were obviously extorted and untrue. We do not make mistakes of\"},{\"text\":\"that kind. All the confessions that are uttered here are true. We make\"}]","[{\"text\":\"them true. And above all we do not allow the dead to rise up against us.\"},{\"text\":\"You must stop imagining that posterity will vindicate you, Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"Posterity will never hear of you. You will be lifted clean out from the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"into gas and pour you into the\"},{\"text\":\"stratosphere. Nothing will remain of you, not a name in a register, not\"},{\"text\":\"a memory in a living brain. You will be annihilated in the past as well\"},{\"text\":\"as in the future. You will never have existed.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Then why bother to torture me? thought Winston, with a momentary\"},{\"text\":\"bitterness. O'Brien checked his step as though Winston had uttered the\"},{\"text\":\"thought aloud. His large ugly face came nearer, with the eyes a little\"},{\"text\":\"narrowed.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'You are thinking,' he said, 'that since we intend to destroy you utterly,\"},{\"text\":\"so that nothing that you say or do can make the smallest difference--in\"},{\"text\":\"that case, why do we go to the trouble of interrogating you first? That is\"},{\"text\":\"what you were thinking, was it not?'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Yes,' said Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien smiled slightly. 'You are a flaw in the pattern, Winston. You are\"},{\"text\":\"a stain that must be wiped out. Did I not tell you just now that we are\"}]","[{\"text\":\"content with\"},{\"text\":\"negative obedience, nor even with the most abject submission. When finally\"},{\"text\":\"you surrender to us, it must be of your own free will. We do not destroy\"},{\"text\":\"the heretic because he resists us: so long as he resists us we never\"}]","[{\"text\":\"convert him, we capture his inner mind, we reshape him.\"},{\"text\":\"We burn all evil and all illusion out of him; we bring him over to our\"},{\"text\":\"side, not in appearance, but genuinely, heart and soul. We make him one of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that an erroneous\"},{\"text\":\"thought should exist anywhere in the world, however secret and powerless\"},{\"text\":\"it may be. Even in the instant of death we cannot permit any deviation. In\"},{\"text\":\"the old days the heretic walked to the stake still a heretic, proclaiming\"}]","[{\"text\":\"exulting in it. Even the victim of the Russian purges could\"},{\"text\":\"carry rebellion locked up in his skull as he walked down the passage\"},{\"text\":\"waiting for the bullet. But we make the brain perfect before we blow it\"}]","[{\"text\":\"despotisms was \\\"Thou shalt not\\\". The command\"},{\"text\":\"of the totalitarians was \\\"Thou shalt\\\". Our command is \\\"THOU ART\\\". No one\"},{\"text\":\"whom we bring to this place ever stands out against us. Everyone is washed\"}]","[{\"text\":\"innocence you once\"},{\"text\":\"believed--Jones, Aaronson, and Rutherford--in the end we broke them down.\"},{\"text\":\"I took part in their interrogation myself. I saw them gradually worn down,\"},{\"text\":\"whimpering, grovelling, weeping--and in the end it was not with pain or\"}]","[{\"text\":\"penitence. By the time we had finished with them they were\"},{\"text\":\"only the shells of men. There was nothing left in them except sorrow for\"},{\"text\":\"what they had done, and love of Big Brother. It was touching to see\"}]","[{\"text\":\"shot quickly, so that they could die\"},{\"text\":\"while their minds were still clean.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"His voice had grown almost dreamy. The exaltation, the lunatic enthusiasm,\"},{\"text\":\"was still in his face. He is not pretending, thought Winston, he is not a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"believes every word he says. What most oppressed him was the\"},{\"text\":\"consciousness of his own intellectual inferiority. He watched the heavy\"},{\"text\":\"yet graceful form strolling to and fro, in and out of the range of his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ways larger than himself. There was no\"},{\"text\":\"idea that he had ever had, or could have, that O'Brien had not long ago\"},{\"text\":\"known, examined, and rejected. His mind CONTAINED Winston's mind. But\"}]","[{\"text\":\"It must be he,\"},{\"text\":\"Winston, who was mad. O'Brien halted and looked down at him. His voice had\"},{\"text\":\"grown stern again.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Do not imagine that you will save yourself, Winston, however completely\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ever spared. And\"},{\"text\":\"even if we chose to let you live out the natural term of your life, still\"},{\"text\":\"you would never escape from us. What happens to you here is for ever.\"},{\"text\":\"Understand that in advance. We shall crush you down to the point from\"}]","[{\"text\":\"coming back. Things will happen to you from which you\"},{\"text\":\"could not recover, if you lived a thousand years. Never again will you be\"},{\"text\":\"capable of ordinary human feeling. Everything will be dead inside you.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"or joy of living,\"},{\"text\":\"or laughter, or curiosity, or courage, or integrity. You will be hollow.\"},{\"text\":\"We shall squeeze you empty, and then we shall fill you with ourselves.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He paused and signed to the man in the white coat. Winston was aware of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"some heavy piece of apparatus being pushed into place behind his head.\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien had sat down beside the bed, so that his face was almost on a\"},{\"text\":\"level with Winston's.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to the man in the\"},{\"text\":\"white coat.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Two soft pads, which felt slightly moist, clamped themselves against\"},{\"text\":\"Winston's temples. He quailed. There was pain coming, a new kind of pain.\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien laid a hand reassuringly, almost kindly, on his.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'This time it will not hurt,' he said. 'Keep your eyes fixed on mine.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"At this moment there was a devastating explosion, or what seemed like an\"},{\"text\":\"explosion, though it was not certain whether there was any noise. There\"}]","[{\"text\":\"blinding flash of light. Winston was not hurt, only\"},{\"text\":\"prostrated. Although he had already been lying on his back when the thing\"},{\"text\":\"happened, he had a curious feeling that he had been knocked into that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"out. Also something\"},{\"text\":\"had happened inside his head. As his eyes regained their focus he\"},{\"text\":\"remembered who he was, and where he was, and recognized the face that was\"},{\"text\":\"gazing into his own; but somewhere or other there was a large patch of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"emptiness, as though a piece had been taken out of his brain.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'It will not last,' said O'Brien. 'Look me in the eyes. What country is\"},{\"text\":\"Oceania at war with?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"meant by Oceania and that he himself was\"},{\"text\":\"a citizen of Oceania. He also remembered Eurasia and Eastasia; but who was\"},{\"text\":\"at war with whom he did not know. In fact he had not been aware that there\"},{\"text\":\"was any war.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I don't remember.'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Oceania is at war with Eastasia. Do you remember that now?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Oceania has always been at war with Eastasia. Since the beginning of your\"}]","[{\"text\":\"beginning of history,\"},{\"text\":\"the war has continued without a break, always the same war. Do you\"},{\"text\":\"remember that?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Eleven years ago you created a legend about three men who had been\"}]","[{\"text\":\"condemned to death for treachery. You pretended that you had seen a piece\"},{\"text\":\"of paper which proved them innocent. No such piece of paper ever existed.\"},{\"text\":\"You invented it, and later you grew to believe in it. You remember now the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"invented it. Do you remember that?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Just now I held up the fingers of my hand to you. You saw five fingers.\"},{\"text\":\"Do you remember that?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"O'Brien held up the fingers of his left hand, with the thumb concealed.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'There are five fingers there. Do you see five fingers?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"scenery of his\"},{\"text\":\"mind changed. He saw five fingers, and there was no deformity. Then\"},{\"text\":\"everything was normal again, and the old fear, the hatred, and the\"},{\"text\":\"bewilderment came crowding back again. But there had been a moment--he did\"}]","[{\"text\":\"thirty seconds, perhaps--of luminous certainty, when\"},{\"text\":\"each new suggestion of O'Brien's had filled up a patch of emptiness and\"},{\"text\":\"become absolute truth, and when two and two could have been three as\"}]","[{\"text\":\"faded but before\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien had dropped his hand; but though he could not recapture it, he\"},{\"text\":\"could remember it, as one remembers a vivid experience at some period of\"},{\"text\":\"one's life when one was in effect a different person.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"said O'Brien, 'that it is at any rate possible.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes,' said Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien stood up with a satisfied air. Over to his left Winston saw the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"plunger of a\"},{\"text\":\"syringe. O'Brien turned to Winston with a smile. In almost the old manner\"},{\"text\":\"he resettled his spectacles on his nose.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Do you remember writing in your diary,' he said, 'that it did not matter\"}]","[{\"text\":\"friend or an enemy, since I was at least a person who\"},{\"text\":\"understood you and could be talked to? You were right. I enjoy talking to\"},{\"text\":\"you. Your mind appeals to me. It resembles my own mind except that you\"}]","[{\"text\":\"end you can ask me\"},{\"text\":\"a few questions, if you choose.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Any question I like?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Anything.' He saw that Winston's eyes were upon the dial. 'It is switched\"},{\"text\":\"off. What is your first question?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'What have you done with Julia?' said Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien smiled again. 'She betrayed you, Winston. Immediately--unreservedly.\"},{\"text\":\"I have seldom seen anyone come over to us so promptly. You would hardly\"}]","[{\"text\":\"you saw her. All her rebelliousness, her deceit, her\"},{\"text\":\"folly, her dirty-mindedness--everything has been burned out of her. It was\"},{\"text\":\"a perfect conversion, a textbook case.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You tortured her?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"O'Brien left this unanswered. 'Next question,' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Does Big Brother exist?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Of course he exists. The Party exists. Big Brother is the embodiment of\"},{\"text\":\"the Party.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the same way as I exist?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You do not exist,' said O'Brien.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Once again the sense of helplessness assailed him. He knew, or he could\"},{\"text\":\"imagine, the arguments which proved his own nonexistence; but they were\"}]","[{\"text\":\"nonsense, they were only a play on words. Did not the statement, 'You do\"},{\"text\":\"not exist', contain a logical absurdity? But what use was it to say so?\"},{\"text\":\"His mind shrivelled as he thought of the unanswerable, mad arguments with\"},{\"text\":\"which O'Brien would demolish him.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'I think I exist,' he said wearily. 'I am conscious of my own identity.\"},{\"text\":\"I was born and I shall die. I have arms and legs. I occupy a particular\"},{\"text\":\"point in space. No other solid object can occupy the same point\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Big Brother exist?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'It is of no importance. He exists.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Will Big Brother ever die?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Of course not. How could he die? Next question.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Brotherhood exist?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'That, Winston, you will never know. If we choose to set you free when we\"},{\"text\":\"have finished with you, and if you live to be ninety years old, still you\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Yes or No. As long\"},{\"text\":\"as you live it will be an unsolved riddle in your mind.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston lay silent. His breast rose and fell a little faster. He still had\"},{\"text\":\"not asked the question that had come into his mind the first. He had got\"}]","[{\"text\":\"it was as though his tongue would not utter it. There\"},{\"text\":\"was a trace of amusement in O'Brien's face. Even his spectacles seemed to\"},{\"text\":\"wear an ironical gleam. He knows, thought Winston suddenly, he knows what\"}]","[{\"text\":\"him:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'What is in Room 101?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The expression on O'Brien's face did not change. He answered drily:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You know what is in Room 101, Winston. Everyone knows what is in\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Room 101.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He raised a finger to the man in the white coat. Evidently the session was\"},{\"text\":\"at an end. A needle jerked into Winston's arm. He sank almost instantly\"},{\"text\":\"into deep sleep.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Chapter 3\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'There are three stages in your reintegration,' said O'Brien. 'There is\"},{\"text\":\"learning, there is understanding, and there is acceptance. It is time for\"},{\"text\":\"you to enter upon the second stage.'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"As always, Winston was lying flat on his back. But of late his bonds were\"},{\"text\":\"looser. They still held him to the bed, but he could move his knees a\"},{\"text\":\"little and could turn his head from side to side and raise his arms from\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to be less of a terror. He could\"},{\"text\":\"evade its pangs if he was quick-witted enough: it was chiefly when he\"},{\"text\":\"showed stupidity that O'Brien pulled the lever. Sometimes they got through\"},{\"text\":\"a whole session without use of the dial. He could not remember how many\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sessions there had been. The whole process seemed to stretch out over a\"},{\"text\":\"long, indefinite time--weeks, possibly--and the intervals between the\"},{\"text\":\"sessions might sometimes have been days, sometimes only an hour or two.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"there,' said O'Brien, 'you have often wondered--you have even\"},{\"text\":\"asked me--why the Ministry of Love should expend so much time and trouble\"},{\"text\":\"on you. And when you were free you were puzzled by what was essentially\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the mechanics of the Society you lived\"},{\"text\":\"in, but not its underlying motives. Do you remember writing in your diary,\"},{\"text\":\"\\\"I understand HOW: I do not understand WHY\\\"? It was when you thought about\"}]","[{\"text\":\"THE BOOK,\"},{\"text\":\"Goldstein's book, or parts of it, at least. Did it tell you anything that\"},{\"text\":\"you did not know already?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You have read it?' said Winston.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"it. No book is\"},{\"text\":\"produced individually, as you know.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Is it true, what it says?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'As description, yes. The programme it sets forth is nonsense. The secret\"}]","[{\"text\":\"enlightenment--ultimately\"},{\"text\":\"a proletarian rebellion--the overthrow of the Party. You foresaw yourself\"},{\"text\":\"that that was what it would say. It is all nonsense. The proletarians will\"},{\"text\":\"never revolt, not in a thousand years or a million. They cannot. I do\"}]","[{\"text\":\"not have to tell you the reason: you know it already. If you have ever\"},{\"text\":\"cherished any dreams of violent insurrection, you must abandon them. There\"},{\"text\":\"is no way in which the Party can be overthrown. The rule of the Party is\"}]","[{\"text\":\"starting-point of your thoughts.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He came closer to the bed. 'For ever!' he repeated. 'And now let us get\"},{\"text\":\"back to the question of \\\"how\\\" and \\\"why\\\". You understand well enough HOW\"}]","[{\"text\":\"cling to power.\"},{\"text\":\"What is our motive? Why should we want power? Go on, speak,' he added as\"},{\"text\":\"Winston remained silent.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Nevertheless Winston did not speak for another moment or two. A feeling of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"faint, mad gleam of enthusiasm had come\"},{\"text\":\"back into O'Brien's face. He knew in advance what O'Brien would say. That\"},{\"text\":\"the Party did not seek power for its own ends, but only for the good of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"mass were frail,\"},{\"text\":\"cowardly creatures who could not endure liberty or face the truth, and\"},{\"text\":\"must be ruled over and systematically deceived by others who were stronger\"},{\"text\":\"than themselves. That the choice for mankind lay between freedom and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that, for the great bulk of mankind, happiness was better.\"},{\"text\":\"That the party was the eternal guardian of the weak, a dedicated sect\"},{\"text\":\"doing evil that good might come, sacrificing its own happiness to that of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston, the terrible thing was that\"},{\"text\":\"when O'Brien said this he would believe it. You could see it in his face.\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien knew everything. A thousand times better than Winston he knew what\"},{\"text\":\"the world was really like, in what degradation the mass of human beings\"}]","[{\"text\":\"lived and by what lies and barbarities the Party kept them there. He had\"},{\"text\":\"understood it all, weighed it all, and it made no difference: all was\"},{\"text\":\"justified by the ultimate purpose. What can you do, thought Winston,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"intelligent than yourself, who gives your\"},{\"text\":\"arguments a fair hearing and then simply persists in his lunacy?\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You are ruling over us for our own good,' he said feebly. 'You believe\"}]","[{\"text\":\"govern themselves, and therefore----'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He started and almost cried out. A pang of pain had shot through his body.\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien had pushed the lever of the dial up to thirty-five.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"he said. 'You should know better than\"},{\"text\":\"to say a thing like that.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He pulled the lever back and continued:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Now I will tell you the answer to my question. It is this. The Party\"}]","[{\"text\":\"entirely for its own sake. We are not interested in the good\"},{\"text\":\"of others; we are interested solely in power. Not wealth or luxury or long\"},{\"text\":\"life or happiness: only power, pure power. What pure power means you will\"}]","[{\"text\":\"different from all the oligarchies of the\"},{\"text\":\"past, in that we know what we are doing. All the others, even those who\"},{\"text\":\"resembled ourselves, were cowards and hypocrites. The German Nazis and the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"methods, but they never\"},{\"text\":\"had the courage to recognize their own motives. They pretended, perhaps\"},{\"text\":\"they even believed, that they had seized power unwillingly and for a\"},{\"text\":\"limited time, and that just round the corner there lay a paradise where\"}]","[{\"text\":\"human beings would be free and equal. We are not like that. We know that\"},{\"text\":\"no one ever seizes power with the intention of relinquishing it. Power is\"},{\"text\":\"not a means, it is an end. One does not establish a dictatorship in order\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the revolution in order to establish\"},{\"text\":\"the dictatorship. The object of persecution is persecution. The object of\"},{\"text\":\"torture is torture. The object of power is power. Now do you begin to\"},{\"text\":\"understand me?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"struck before, by the tiredness of\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien's face. It was strong and fleshy and brutal, it was full of\"},{\"text\":\"intelligence and a sort of controlled passion before which he felt himself\"},{\"text\":\"helpless; but it was tired. There were pouches under the eyes, the skin\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sagged from the cheekbones. O'Brien leaned over him, deliberately bringing\"},{\"text\":\"the worn face nearer.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You are thinking,' he said, 'that my face is old and tired. You are\"}]","[{\"text\":\"able to prevent the\"},{\"text\":\"decay of my own body. Can you not understand, Winston, that the individual\"},{\"text\":\"is only a cell? The weariness of the cell is the vigour of the organism.\"},{\"text\":\"Do you die when you cut your fingernails?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He turned away from the bed and began strolling up and down again, one hand\"},{\"text\":\"in his pocket.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'We are the priests of power,' he said. 'God is power. But at present\"},{\"text\":\"power is only a word so far as you are concerned. It is time for you to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"gather some idea of what power means. The first thing you must realize\"},{\"text\":\"is that power is collective. The individual only has power in so far as\"},{\"text\":\"he ceases to be an individual. You know the Party slogan: \\\"Freedom is\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that it is reversible? Slavery is\"},{\"text\":\"freedom. Alone--free--the human being is always defeated. It must be so,\"},{\"text\":\"because every human being is doomed to die, which is the greatest of all\"},{\"text\":\"failures. But if he can make complete, utter submission, if he can escape\"}]","[{\"text\":\"from his identity, if he can merge himself in the Party so that he IS the\"},{\"text\":\"Party, then he is all-powerful and immortal. The second thing for you to\"},{\"text\":\"realize is that power is power over human beings. Over the body--but, above\"}]","[{\"text\":\"matter--external reality, as you would call\"},{\"text\":\"it--is not important. Already our control over matter is absolute.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"For a moment Winston ignored the dial. He made a violent effort to raise\"}]","[{\"text\":\"merely succeeded in wrenching his\"},{\"text\":\"body painfully.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'But how can you control matter?' he burst out. 'You don't even control\"},{\"text\":\"the climate or the law of gravity. And there are disease, pain, death----'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"him by a movement of his hand. 'We control matter because\"},{\"text\":\"we control the mind. Reality is inside the skull. You will learn by\"},{\"text\":\"degrees, Winston. There is nothing that we could not do. Invisibility,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"off this floor like a soap bubble if\"},{\"text\":\"I wish to. I do not wish to, because the Party does not wish it. You must\"},{\"text\":\"get rid of those nineteenth-century ideas about the laws of Nature. We\"},{\"text\":\"make the laws of Nature.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"You are not even masters of this planet. What about\"},{\"text\":\"Eurasia and Eastasia? You have not conquered them yet.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Unimportant. We shall conquer them when it suits us. And if we did not,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"existence. Oceania\"},{\"text\":\"is the world.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'But the world itself is only a speck of dust. And man is tiny--helpless!\"},{\"text\":\"How long has he been in existence? For millions of years the earth was\"},{\"text\":\"uninhabited.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"earth is as old as we are, no older. How could it be older?\"},{\"text\":\"Nothing exists except through human consciousness.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'But the rocks are full of the bones of extinct animals--mammoths and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"lived here long before man was ever\"},{\"text\":\"heard of.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Have you ever seen those bones, Winston? Of course not. Nineteenth-century\"},{\"text\":\"biologists invented them. Before man there was nothing. After man, if he\"}]","[{\"text\":\"nothing. Outside man there is\"},{\"text\":\"nothing.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'But the whole universe is outside us. Look at the stars! Some of them are\"},{\"text\":\"a million light-years away. They are out of our reach for ever.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"stars?' said O'Brien indifferently. 'They are bits of fire\"},{\"text\":\"a few kilometres away. We could reach them if we wanted to. Or we could\"},{\"text\":\"blot them out. The earth is the centre of the universe. The sun and the\"},{\"text\":\"stars go round it.'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston made another convulsive movement. This time he did not say\"},{\"text\":\"anything. O'Brien continued as though answering a spoken objection:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'For certain purposes, of course, that is not true. When we navigate the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"predict an eclipse, we often find it convenient to\"},{\"text\":\"assume that the earth goes round the sun and that the stars are millions\"},{\"text\":\"upon millions of kilometres away. But what of it? Do you suppose it is\"}]","[{\"text\":\"stars can be near\"},{\"text\":\"or distant, according as we need them. Do you suppose our mathematicians\"},{\"text\":\"are unequal to that? Have you forgotten doublethink?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston shrank back upon the bed. Whatever he said, the swift answer\"}]","[{\"text\":\"bludgeon. And yet he knew, he KNEW, that he was in the\"},{\"text\":\"right. The belief that nothing exists outside your own mind--surely there\"},{\"text\":\"must be some way of demonstrating that it was false? Had it not been\"}]","[{\"text\":\"it, which he\"},{\"text\":\"had forgotten. A faint smile twitched the corners of O'Brien's mouth as\"},{\"text\":\"he looked down at him.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I told you, Winston,' he said, 'that metaphysics is not your strong\"}]","[{\"text\":\"think of is solipsism. But you are\"},{\"text\":\"mistaken. This is not solipsism. Collective solipsism, if you like. But\"},{\"text\":\"that is a different thing: in fact, the opposite thing. All this is a\"},{\"text\":\"digression,' he added in a different tone. 'The real power, the power we\"}]","[{\"text\":\"have to fight for night and day, is not power over things, but over men.'\"},{\"text\":\"He paused, and for a moment assumed again his air of a schoolmaster\"},{\"text\":\"questioning a promising pupil: 'How does one man assert his power over\"},{\"text\":\"another, Winston?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Winston thought. 'By making him suffer,' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Exactly. By making him suffer. Obedience is not enough. Unless he is\"},{\"text\":\"suffering, how can you be sure that he is obeying your will and not his\"}]","[{\"text\":\"humiliation. Power is in tearing\"},{\"text\":\"human minds to pieces and putting them together again in new shapes of\"},{\"text\":\"your own choosing. Do you begin to see, then, what kind of world we are\"},{\"text\":\"creating? It is the exact opposite of the stupid hedonistic Utopias that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the old reformers imagined. A world of fear and treachery and torment, a\"},{\"text\":\"world of trampling and being trampled upon, a world which will grow not\"},{\"text\":\"less but MORE merciless as it refines itself. Progress in our world will\"}]","[{\"text\":\"old civilizations claimed that they\"},{\"text\":\"were founded on love or justice. Ours is founded upon hatred. In our world\"},{\"text\":\"there will be no emotions except fear, rage, triumph, and self-abasement.\"},{\"text\":\"Everything else we shall destroy--everything. Already we are breaking down\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the habits of thought which have survived from before the Revolution. We\"},{\"text\":\"have cut the links between child and parent, and between man and man, and\"},{\"text\":\"between man and woman. No one dares trust a wife or a child or a friend\"}]","[{\"text\":\"will be no wives and no friends.\"},{\"text\":\"Children will be taken from their mothers at birth, as one takes eggs from\"},{\"text\":\"a hen. The sex instinct will be eradicated. Procreation will be an annual\"},{\"text\":\"formality like the renewal of a ration card. We shall abolish the orgasm.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Our neurologists are at work upon it now. There will be no loyalty, except\"},{\"text\":\"loyalty towards the Party. There will be no love, except the love of\"},{\"text\":\"Big Brother. There will be no laughter, except the laugh of triumph over\"}]","[{\"text\":\"art, no literature, no science. When\"},{\"text\":\"we are omnipotent we shall have no more need of science. There will be\"},{\"text\":\"no distinction between beauty and ugliness. There will be no curiosity,\"},{\"text\":\"no enjoyment of the process of life. All competing pleasures will be\"}]","[{\"text\":\"destroyed. But always--do not forget this, Winston--always there will be\"},{\"text\":\"the intoxication of power, constantly increasing and constantly growing\"},{\"text\":\"subtler. Always, at every moment, there will be the thrill of victory,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"enemy who is helpless. If you want a\"},{\"text\":\"picture of the future, imagine a boot stamping on a human face--for ever.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He paused as though he expected Winston to speak. Winston had tried to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"not say anything.\"},{\"text\":\"His heart seemed to be frozen. O'Brien went on:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'And remember that it is for ever. The face will always be there to be\"},{\"text\":\"stamped upon. The heretic, the enemy of society, will always be there, so\"}]","[{\"text\":\"defeated and humiliated over again. Everything that you\"},{\"text\":\"have undergone since you have been in our hands--all that will continue,\"},{\"text\":\"and worse. The espionage, the betrayals, the arrests, the tortures, the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"be a world of\"},{\"text\":\"terror as much as a world of triumph. The more the Party is powerful, the\"},{\"text\":\"less it will be tolerant: the weaker the opposition, the tighter the\"},{\"text\":\"despotism. Goldstein and his heresies will live for ever. Every day, at\"}]","[{\"text\":\"will be defeated, discredited, ridiculed, spat upon and\"},{\"text\":\"yet they will always survive. This drama that I have played out with you\"},{\"text\":\"during seven years will be played out over and over again generation after\"}]","[{\"text\":\"have the heretic here\"},{\"text\":\"at our mercy, screaming with pain, broken up, contemptible--and in the end\"},{\"text\":\"utterly penitent, saved from himself, crawling to our feet of his own\"},{\"text\":\"accord. That is the world that we are preparing, Winston. A world of\"}]","[{\"text\":\"victory after victory, triumph after triumph after triumph: an endless\"},{\"text\":\"pressing, pressing, pressing upon the nerve of power. You are beginning,\"},{\"text\":\"I can see, to realize what that world will be like. But in the end you\"}]","[{\"text\":\"will accept it, welcome it, become\"},{\"text\":\"part of it.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston had recovered himself sufficiently to speak. 'You can't!' he said\"},{\"text\":\"weakly.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'What do you mean by that remark, Winston?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'You could not create such a world as you have just described. It is a\"},{\"text\":\"dream. It is impossible.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Why?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'It is impossible to found a civilization on fear and hatred and cruelty.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"endure.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Why not?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'It would have no vitality. It would disintegrate. It would commit\"},{\"text\":\"suicide.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Nonsense. You are under the impression that hatred is more exhausting\"}]","[{\"text\":\"than love. Why should it be? And if it were, what difference would that\"},{\"text\":\"make? Suppose that we choose to wear ourselves out faster. Suppose that we\"},{\"text\":\"quicken the tempo of human life till men are senile at thirty. Still what\"}]","[{\"text\":\"understand that the death of the\"},{\"text\":\"individual is not death? The party is immortal.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"As usual, the voice had battered Winston into helplessness. Moreover he\"},{\"text\":\"was in dread that if he persisted in his disagreement O'Brien would twist\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the dial again. And yet he could not keep silent. Feebly, without\"},{\"text\":\"arguments, with nothing to support him except his inarticulate horror of\"},{\"text\":\"what O'Brien had said, he returned to the attack.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"you will fail. Something will defeat\"},{\"text\":\"you. Life will defeat you.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'We control life, Winston, at all its levels. You are imagining that there\"},{\"text\":\"is something called human nature which will be outraged by what we do and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"us. But we create human nature. Men are infinitely\"},{\"text\":\"malleable. Or perhaps you have returned to your old idea that the\"},{\"text\":\"proletarians or the slaves will arise and overthrow us. Put it out of your\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the Party. The\"},{\"text\":\"others are outside--irrelevant.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I don't care. In the end they will beat you. Sooner or later they will\"},{\"text\":\"see you for what you are, and then they will tear you to pieces.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"evidence that that is happening? Or any reason why it\"},{\"text\":\"should?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No. I believe it. I KNOW that you will fail. There is something in the\"},{\"text\":\"universe--I don't know, some spirit, some principle--that you will never\"},{\"text\":\"overcome.'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Do you believe in God, Winston?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'No.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Then what is it, this principle that will defeat us?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I don't know. The spirit of Man.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'And do you consider yourself a man?'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Yes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'If you are a man, Winston, you are the last man. Your kind is extinct; we\"},{\"text\":\"are the inheritors. Do you understand that you are ALONE? You are outside\"},{\"text\":\"history, you are non-existent.' His manner changed and he said more\"}]","[{\"text\":\"harshly: 'And you consider yourself morally superior to us, with our lies\"},{\"text\":\"and our cruelty?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Yes, I consider myself superior.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien did not speak. Two other voices were speaking. After a moment\"}]","[{\"text\":\"one of them as his own. It was a sound-track of the\"},{\"text\":\"conversation he had had with O'Brien, on the night when he had enrolled\"},{\"text\":\"himself in the Brotherhood. He heard himself promising to lie, to steal,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"prostitution, to\"},{\"text\":\"disseminate venereal diseases, to throw vitriol in a child's face. O'Brien\"},{\"text\":\"made a small impatient gesture, as though to say that the demonstration\"},{\"text\":\"was hardly worth making. Then he turned a switch and the voices stopped.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Get up from that bed,' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The bonds had loosened themselves. Winston lowered himself to the floor\"},{\"text\":\"and stood up unsteadily.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You are the last man,' said O'Brien. 'You are the guardian of the human\"}]","[{\"text\":\"spirit. You shall see yourself as you are. Take off your clothes.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston undid the bit of string that held his overalls together. The zip\"},{\"text\":\"fastener had long since been wrenched out of them. He could not remember\"}]","[{\"text\":\"time since his arrest he had taken off all his clothes at\"},{\"text\":\"one time. Beneath the overalls his body was looped with filthy yellowish\"},{\"text\":\"rags, just recognizable as the remnants of underclothes. As he slid\"}]","[{\"text\":\"was a three-sided mirror at the far\"},{\"text\":\"end of the room. He approached it, then stopped short. An involuntary cry\"},{\"text\":\"had broken out of him.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Go on,' said O'Brien. 'Stand between the wings of the mirror. You shall\"}]","[{\"text\":\"as well.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He had stopped because he was frightened. A bowed, grey-coloured,\"},{\"text\":\"skeleton-like thing was coming towards him. Its actual appearance was\"},{\"text\":\"frightening, and not merely the fact that he knew it to be himself. He\"}]","[{\"text\":\"moved closer to the glass. The creature's face seemed to be protruded,\"},{\"text\":\"because of its bent carriage. A forlorn, jailbird's face with a nobby\"},{\"text\":\"forehead running back into a bald scalp, a crooked nose, and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"which his eyes were fierce and watchful.\"},{\"text\":\"The cheeks were seamed, the mouth had a drawn-in look. Certainly it was\"},{\"text\":\"his own face, but it seemed to him that it had changed more than he had\"}]","[{\"text\":\"different from the\"},{\"text\":\"ones he felt. He had gone partially bald. For the first moment he had\"},{\"text\":\"thought that he had gone grey as well, but it was only the scalp that was\"},{\"text\":\"grey. Except for his hands and a circle of his face, his body was grey all\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ingrained dirt. Here and there under the dirt there\"},{\"text\":\"were the red scars of wounds, and near the ankle the varicose ulcer was an\"},{\"text\":\"inflamed mass with flakes of skin peeling off it. But the truly frightening\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ribs was as narrow\"},{\"text\":\"as that of a skeleton: the legs had shrunk so that the knees were thicker\"},{\"text\":\"than the thighs. He saw now what O'Brien had meant about seeing the side\"},{\"text\":\"view. The curvature of the spine was astonishing. The thin shoulders were\"}]","[{\"text\":\"as to make a cavity of the chest, the scraggy neck\"},{\"text\":\"seemed to be bending double under the weight of the skull. At a guess he\"},{\"text\":\"would have said that it was the body of a man of sixty, suffering from\"},{\"text\":\"some malignant disease.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'You have thought sometimes,' said O'Brien, 'that my face--the face of a\"},{\"text\":\"member of the Inner Party--looks old and worn. What do you think of your\"},{\"text\":\"own face?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He seized Winston's shoulder and spun him round so that he was facing him.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'Look at the condition you are in!' he said. 'Look at this filthy grime\"},{\"text\":\"all over your body. Look at the dirt between your toes. Look at that\"},{\"text\":\"disgusting running sore on your leg. Do you know that you stink like a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"notice it. Look at your emaciation. Do\"},{\"text\":\"you see? I can make my thumb and forefinger meet round your bicep. I could\"},{\"text\":\"snap your neck like a carrot. Do you know that you have lost twenty-five\"}]","[{\"text\":\"hair is coming out\"},{\"text\":\"in handfuls. Look!' He plucked at Winston's head and brought away a tuft\"},{\"text\":\"of hair. 'Open your mouth. Nine, ten, eleven teeth left. How many had you\"},{\"text\":\"when you came to us? And the few you have left are dropping out of your\"},{\"text\":\"head. Look here!'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He seized one of Winston's remaining front teeth between his powerful\"},{\"text\":\"thumb and forefinger. A twinge of pain shot through Winston's jaw. O'Brien\"},{\"text\":\"had wrenched the loose tooth out by the roots. He tossed it across the\"},{\"text\":\"cell.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'You are rotting away,' he said; 'you are falling to pieces. What are you?\"},{\"text\":\"A bag of filth. Now turn around and look into that mirror again. Do you\"},{\"text\":\"see that thing facing you? That is the last man. If you are human, that is\"}]","[{\"text\":\"again.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Winston began to dress himself with slow stiff movements. Until now he had\"},{\"text\":\"not seemed to notice how thin and weak he was. Only one thought stirred in\"},{\"text\":\"his mind: that he must have been in this place longer than he had imagined.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Then suddenly as he fixed the miserable rags round himself a feeling of\"},{\"text\":\"pity for his ruined body overcame him. Before he knew what he was doing\"},{\"text\":\"he had collapsed on to a small stool that stood beside the bed and burst\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ugliness, his gracelessness, a bundle of\"},{\"text\":\"bones in filthy underclothes sitting weeping in the harsh white light: but\"},{\"text\":\"he could not stop himself. O'Brien laid a hand on his shoulder, almost\"},{\"text\":\"kindly.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"for ever,' he said. 'You can escape from it whenever you\"},{\"text\":\"choose. Everything depends on yourself.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You did it!' sobbed Winston. 'You reduced me to this state.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"it. This is what you accepted when\"},{\"text\":\"you set yourself up against the Party. It was all contained in that first\"},{\"text\":\"act. Nothing has happened that you did not foresee.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He paused, and then went on:\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"you, Winston. We have broken you up. You have seen what\"},{\"text\":\"your body is like. Your mind is in the same state. I do not think there\"},{\"text\":\"can be much pride left in you. You have been kicked and flogged and\"}]","[{\"text\":\"on the floor in\"},{\"text\":\"your own blood and vomit. You have whimpered for mercy, you have betrayed\"},{\"text\":\"everybody and everything. Can you think of a single degradation that has\"},{\"text\":\"not happened to you?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the tears were still oozing out of his\"},{\"text\":\"eyes. He looked up at O'Brien.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I have not betrayed Julia,' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien looked down at him thoughtfully. 'No,' he said; 'no; that is\"}]","[{\"text\":\"You have not betrayed Julia.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The peculiar reverence for O'Brien, which nothing seemed able to destroy,\"},{\"text\":\"flooded Winston's heart again. How intelligent, he thought, how\"}]","[{\"text\":\"was said to him.\"},{\"text\":\"Anyone else on earth would have answered promptly that he HAD betrayed\"},{\"text\":\"Julia. For what was there that they had not screwed out of him under the\"},{\"text\":\"torture? He had told them everything he knew about her, her habits, her\"}]","[{\"text\":\"past life; he had confessed in the most trivial detail\"},{\"text\":\"everything that had happened at their meetings, all that he had said to\"},{\"text\":\"her and she to him, their black-market meals, their adulteries, their\"}]","[{\"text\":\"in the sense in\"},{\"text\":\"which he intended the word, he had not betrayed her. He had not stopped\"},{\"text\":\"loving her; his feelings towards her had remained the same. O'Brien had\"},{\"text\":\"seen what he meant without the need for explanation.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"said, 'how soon will they shoot me?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'It might be a long time,' said O'Brien. 'You are a difficult case. But\"},{\"text\":\"don't give up hope. Everyone is cured sooner or later. In the end we shall\"},{\"text\":\"shoot you.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Chapter 4\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He was much better. He was growing fatter and stronger every day, if it\"},{\"text\":\"was proper to speak of days.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ever, but the cell\"},{\"text\":\"was a little more comfortable than the others he had been in. There was a\"},{\"text\":\"pillow and a mattress on the plank bed, and a stool to sit on. They had\"},{\"text\":\"given him a bath, and they allowed him to wash himself fairly frequently\"}]","[{\"text\":\"They even gave him warm water to wash with. They had given\"},{\"text\":\"him new underclothes and a clean suit of overalls. They had dressed his\"},{\"text\":\"varicose ulcer with soothing ointment. They had pulled out the remnants\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of dentures.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Weeks or months must have passed. It would have been possible now to keep\"},{\"text\":\"count of the passage of time, if he had felt any interest in doing so,\"},{\"text\":\"since he was being fed at what appeared to be regular intervals. He was\"}]","[{\"text\":\"getting, he judged, three meals in the twenty-four hours; sometimes he\"},{\"text\":\"wondered dimly whether he was getting them by night or by day. The food\"},{\"text\":\"was surprisingly good, with meat at every third meal. Once there was even\"}]","[{\"text\":\"matches, but the never-speaking guard\"},{\"text\":\"who brought his food would give him a light. The first time he tried to\"},{\"text\":\"smoke it made him sick, but he persevered, and spun the packet out for\"},{\"text\":\"a long time, smoking half a cigarette after each meal.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"They had given him a white slate with a stump of pencil tied to the\"},{\"text\":\"corner. At first he made no use of it. Even when he was awake he was\"},{\"text\":\"completely torpid. Often he would lie from one meal to the next almost\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sometimes waking into vague reveries\"},{\"text\":\"in which it was too much trouble to open his eyes. He had long grown\"},{\"text\":\"used to sleeping with a strong light on his face. It seemed to make no\"},{\"text\":\"difference, except that one's dreams were more coherent. He dreamed a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"great deal all through this time, and they were always happy dreams. He\"},{\"text\":\"was in the Golden Country, or he was sitting among enormous glorious,\"},{\"text\":\"sunlit ruins, with his mother, with Julia, with O'Brien--not doing\"}]","[{\"text\":\"talking of peaceful things. Such\"},{\"text\":\"thoughts as he had when he was awake were mostly about his dreams. He\"},{\"text\":\"seemed to have lost the power of intellectual effort, now that the\"},{\"text\":\"stimulus of pain had been removed. He was not bored, he had no desire\"}]","[{\"text\":\"for conversation or distraction. Merely to be alone, not to be beaten\"},{\"text\":\"or questioned, to have enough to eat, and to be clean all over, was\"},{\"text\":\"completely satisfying.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"still felt no\"},{\"text\":\"impulse to get off the bed. All he cared for was to lie quiet and feel the\"},{\"text\":\"strength gathering in his body. He would finger himself here and there,\"},{\"text\":\"trying to make sure that it was not an illusion that his muscles were\"}]","[{\"text\":\"and his skin tauter. Finally it was established beyond a\"},{\"text\":\"doubt that he was growing fatter; his thighs were now definitely thicker\"},{\"text\":\"than his knees. After that, reluctantly at first, he began exercising\"}]","[{\"text\":\"kilometres,\"},{\"text\":\"measured by pacing the cell, and his bowed shoulders were growing\"},{\"text\":\"straighter. He attempted more elaborate exercises, and was astonished and\"},{\"text\":\"humiliated to find what things he could not do. He could not move out of a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"hold his stool out at arm's length, he could not stand\"},{\"text\":\"on one leg without falling over. He squatted down on his heels, and found\"},{\"text\":\"that with agonizing pains in thigh and calf he could just lift himself to\"}]","[{\"text\":\"to lift his weight\"},{\"text\":\"by his hands. It was hopeless, he could not raise himself a centimetre.\"},{\"text\":\"But after a few more days--a few more mealtimes--even that feat was\"},{\"text\":\"accomplished. A time came when he could do it six times running. He began\"}]","[{\"text\":\"proud of his body, and to cherish an intermittent belief\"},{\"text\":\"that his face also was growing back to normal. Only when he chanced to put\"},{\"text\":\"his hand on his bald scalp did he remember the seamed, ruined face that\"},{\"text\":\"had looked back at him out of the mirror.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"His mind grew more active. He sat down on the plank bed, his back against\"},{\"text\":\"the wall and the slate on his knees, and set to work deliberately at the\"},{\"text\":\"task of re-educating himself.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"saw now, he had\"},{\"text\":\"been ready to capitulate long before he had taken the decision. From the\"},{\"text\":\"moment when he was inside the Ministry of Love--and yes, even during those\"},{\"text\":\"minutes when he and Julia had stood helpless while the iron voice from the\"}]","[{\"text\":\"them what to do--he had grasped the frivolity, the\"},{\"text\":\"shallowness of his attempt to set himself up against the power of the\"},{\"text\":\"Party. He knew now that for seven years the Thought Police had watched him\"}]","[{\"text\":\"physical act, no word\"},{\"text\":\"spoken aloud, that they had not noticed, no train of thought that they had\"},{\"text\":\"not been able to infer. Even the speck of whitish dust on the cover of his\"},{\"text\":\"diary they had carefully replaced. They had played sound-tracks to him,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"shown him photographs. Some of them were photographs of Julia and himself.\"},{\"text\":\"Yes, even... He could not fight against the Party any longer. Besides,\"},{\"text\":\"the Party was in the right. It must be so; how could the immortal,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"external standard could you check\"},{\"text\":\"its judgements? Sanity was statistical. It was merely a question of\"},{\"text\":\"learning to think as they thought. Only----!\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"The pencil felt thick and awkward in his fingers. He began to write down\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the thoughts that came into his head. He wrote first in large clumsy\"},{\"text\":\"capitals:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"FREEDOM IS SLAVERY\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Then almost without a pause he wrote beneath it:\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"TWO AND TWO MAKE FIVE\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"But then there came a sort of check. His mind, as though shying away from\"},{\"text\":\"something, seemed unable to concentrate. He knew that he knew what came\"}]","[{\"text\":\"recall it. When he did recall it,\"},{\"text\":\"it was only by consciously reasoning out what it must be: it did not come\"},{\"text\":\"of its own accord. He wrote:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"GOD IS POWER\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"everything. The past was alterable. The past never had been\"},{\"text\":\"altered. Oceania was at war with Eastasia. Oceania had always been at war\"},{\"text\":\"with Eastasia. Jones, Aaronson, and Rutherford were guilty of the crimes\"}]","[{\"text\":\"seen the photograph that disproved\"},{\"text\":\"their guilt. It had never existed, he had invented it. He remembered\"},{\"text\":\"remembering contrary things, but those were false memories, products of\"},{\"text\":\"self-deception. How easy it all was! Only surrender, and everything else\"}]","[{\"text\":\"followed. It was like swimming against a current that swept you backwards\"},{\"text\":\"however hard you struggled, and then suddenly deciding to turn round and\"},{\"text\":\"go with the current instead of opposing it. Nothing had changed except\"}]","[{\"text\":\"thing happened in any case. He hardly\"},{\"text\":\"knew why he had ever rebelled. Everything was easy, except----!\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Anything could be true. The so-called laws of Nature were nonsense. The\"}]","[{\"text\":\"said, 'I could\"},{\"text\":\"float off this floor like a soap bubble.' Winston worked it out. 'If he\"},{\"text\":\"THINKS he floats off the floor, and if I simultaneously THINK I see him\"},{\"text\":\"do it, then the thing happens.' Suddenly, like a lump of submerged wreckage\"}]","[{\"text\":\"surface of water, the thought burst into his mind: 'It doesn't\"},{\"text\":\"really happen. We imagine it. It is hallucination.' He pushed the thought\"},{\"text\":\"under instantly. The fallacy was obvious. It presupposed that somewhere\"}]","[{\"text\":\"a 'real' world where 'real' things\"},{\"text\":\"happened. But how could there be such a world? What knowledge have we of\"},{\"text\":\"anything, save through our own minds? All happenings are in the mind.\"},{\"text\":\"Whatever happens in all minds, truly happens.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He had no difficulty in disposing of the fallacy, and he was in no danger\"},{\"text\":\"of succumbing to it. He realized, nevertheless, that it ought never to\"},{\"text\":\"have occurred to him. The mind should develop a blind spot whenever a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"The process should be automatic,\"},{\"text\":\"instinctive. CRIMESTOP, they called it in Newspeak.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He set to work to exercise himself in crimestop. He presented himself with\"},{\"text\":\"propositions--'the Party says the earth is flat', 'the party says that\"}]","[{\"text\":\"ice is heavier than water'--and trained himself in not seeing or not\"},{\"text\":\"understanding the arguments that contradicted them. It was not easy.\"},{\"text\":\"It needed great powers of reasoning and improvisation. The arithmetical\"}]","[{\"text\":\"such a statement as 'two and two make\"},{\"text\":\"five' were beyond his intellectual grasp. It needed also a sort of\"},{\"text\":\"athleticism of mind, an ability at one moment to make the most delicate\"},{\"text\":\"use of logic and at the next to be unconscious of the crudest logical\"}]","[{\"text\":\"errors. Stupidity was as necessary as intelligence, and as difficult to\"},{\"text\":\"attain.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"All the while, with one part of his mind, he wondered how soon they would\"},{\"text\":\"shoot him. 'Everything depends on yourself,' O'Brien had said; but he knew\"}]","[{\"text\":\"that there was no conscious act by which he could bring it nearer. It\"},{\"text\":\"might be ten minutes hence, or ten years. They might keep him for years in\"},{\"text\":\"solitary confinement, they might send him to a labour-camp, they might\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sometimes did. It was perfectly possible\"},{\"text\":\"that before he was shot the whole drama of his arrest and interrogation\"},{\"text\":\"would be enacted all over again. The one certain thing was that death\"}]","[{\"text\":\"unspoken tradition:\"},{\"text\":\"somehow you knew it, though you never heard it said--was that they shot\"},{\"text\":\"you from behind; always in the back of the head, without warning, as you\"},{\"text\":\"walked down a corridor from cell to cell.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"One day--but 'one day' was not the right expression; just as probably it\"},{\"text\":\"was in the middle of the night: once--he fell into a strange, blissful\"},{\"text\":\"reverie. He was walking down the corridor, waiting for the bullet. He knew\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Everything was settled, smoothed\"},{\"text\":\"out, reconciled. There were no more doubts, no more arguments, no more\"},{\"text\":\"pain, no more fear. His body was healthy and strong. He walked easily,\"},{\"text\":\"with a joy of movement and with a feeling of walking in sunlight. He was\"}]","[{\"text\":\"not any longer in the narrow white corridors in the Ministry of Love, he\"},{\"text\":\"was in the enormous sunlit passage, a kilometre wide, down which he had\"},{\"text\":\"seemed to walk in the delirium induced by drugs. He was in the Golden\"}]","[{\"text\":\"across the old rabbit-cropped pasture.\"},{\"text\":\"He could feel the short springy turf under his feet and the gentle sunshine\"},{\"text\":\"on his face. At the edge of the field were the elm trees, faintly stirring,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"lay in the green\"},{\"text\":\"pools under the willows.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"Suddenly he started up with a shock of horror. The sweat broke out on his\"},{\"text\":\"backbone. He had heard himself cry aloud:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Julia! Julia! Julia, my love! Julia!'\"}]","[{\"text\":\"For a moment he had had an overwhelming hallucination of her presence. She\"},{\"text\":\"had seemed to be not merely with him, but inside him. It was as though she\"},{\"text\":\"had got into the texture of his skin. In that moment he had loved her far\"}]","[{\"text\":\"were together and free. Also he knew\"},{\"text\":\"that somewhere or other she was still alive and needed his help.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He lay back on the bed and tried to compose himself. What had he done? How\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of weakness?\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"In another moment he would hear the tramp of boots outside. They could not\"},{\"text\":\"let such an outburst go unpunished. They would know now, if they had not\"},{\"text\":\"known before, that he was breaking the agreement he had made with them.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He obeyed the Party, but he still hated the Party. In the old days he had\"},{\"text\":\"hidden a heretical mind beneath an appearance of conformity. Now he had\"},{\"text\":\"retreated a step further: in the mind he had surrendered, but he had hoped\"}]","[{\"text\":\"knew that he was in the wrong, but\"},{\"text\":\"he preferred to be in the wrong. They would understand that--O'Brien would\"},{\"text\":\"understand it. It was all confessed in that single foolish cry.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"years. He ran a hand\"},{\"text\":\"over his face, trying to familiarize himself with the new shape. There\"},{\"text\":\"were deep furrows in the cheeks, the cheekbones felt sharp, the nose\"},{\"text\":\"flattened. Besides, since last seeing himself in the glass he had been\"}]","[{\"text\":\"given a complete new set of teeth. It was not easy to preserve\"},{\"text\":\"inscrutability when you did not know what your face looked like. In any\"},{\"text\":\"case, mere control of the features was not enough. For the first time he\"}]","[{\"text\":\"secret you must also hide it from\"},{\"text\":\"yourself. You must know all the while that it is there, but until it is\"},{\"text\":\"needed you must never let it emerge into your consciousness in any shape\"},{\"text\":\"that could be given a name. From now onwards he must not only think right;\"}]","[{\"text\":\"he must feel right, dream right. And all the while he must keep his hatred\"},{\"text\":\"locked up inside him like a ball of matter which was part of himself and\"},{\"text\":\"yet unconnected with the rest of him, a kind of cyst.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"him. You could not tell when it would\"},{\"text\":\"happen, but a few seconds beforehand it should be possible to guess. It\"},{\"text\":\"was always from behind, walking down a corridor. Ten seconds would be\"},{\"text\":\"enough. In that time the world inside him could turn over. And then\"}]","[{\"text\":\"suddenly, without a word uttered, without a check in his step, without the\"},{\"text\":\"changing of a line in his face--suddenly the camouflage would be down and\"},{\"text\":\"bang! would go the batteries of his hatred. Hatred would fill him like an\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the same instant bang! would go the\"},{\"text\":\"bullet, too late, or too early. They would have blown his brain to pieces\"},{\"text\":\"before they could reclaim it. The heretical thought would be unpunished,\"},{\"text\":\"unrepented, out of their reach for ever. They would have blown a hole in\"}]","[{\"text\":\"their own perfection. To die hating them, that was freedom.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He shut his eyes. It was more difficult than accepting an intellectual\"},{\"text\":\"discipline. It was a question of degrading himself, mutilating himself. He\"}]","[{\"text\":\"into the filthiest of filth. What was the most horrible,\"},{\"text\":\"sickening thing of all? He thought of Big Brother. The enormous face\"},{\"text\":\"(because of constantly seeing it on posters he always thought of it as\"}]","[{\"text\":\"the eyes that\"},{\"text\":\"followed you to and fro, seemed to float into his mind of its own accord.\"},{\"text\":\"What were his true feelings towards Big Brother?\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"There was a heavy tramp of boots in the passage. The steel door swung open\"}]","[{\"text\":\"O'Brien walked into the cell. Behind him were the waxen-faced\"},{\"text\":\"officer and the black-uniformed guards.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Get up,' said O'Brien. 'Come here.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"shoulders between his\"},{\"text\":\"strong hands and looked at him closely.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You have had thoughts of deceiving me,' he said. 'That was stupid.\"},{\"text\":\"Stand up straighter. Look me in the face.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He paused, and went on in a gentler tone:\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You are improving. Intellectually there is very little wrong with you.\"},{\"text\":\"It is only emotionally that you have failed to make progress. Tell me,\"}]","[{\"text\":\"know that I am always able to detect\"},{\"text\":\"a lie--tell me, what are your true feelings towards Big Brother?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'I hate him.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'You hate him. Good. Then the time has come for you to take the last step.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Brother. It is not enough to obey him: you must love\"},{\"text\":\"him.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"He released Winston with a little push towards the guards.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Room 101,' he said.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"Chapter 5\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"At each stage of his imprisonment he had known, or seemed to know,\"},{\"text\":\"whereabouts he was in the windowless building. Possibly there were slight\"}]","[{\"text\":\"cells where the guards had beaten him\"},{\"text\":\"were below ground level. The room where he had been interrogated by\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien was high up near the roof. This place was many metres underground,\"},{\"text\":\"as deep down as it was possible to go.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"It was bigger than most of the cells he had been in. But he hardly noticed\"},{\"text\":\"his surroundings. All he noticed was that there were two small tables\"},{\"text\":\"straight in front of him, each covered with green baize. One was only a\"}]","[{\"text\":\"further away, near the door. He was\"},{\"text\":\"strapped upright in a chair, so tightly that he could move nothing, not\"},{\"text\":\"even his head. A sort of pad gripped his head from behind, forcing him to\"},{\"text\":\"look straight in front of him.\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","