 a high cracked voice. 'You couldn't,\"},{\"text\":\"you couldn't! It's impossible.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'Do you remember,' said O'Brien, 'the moment of panic that used to occur\"}]","[{\"text\":\"of you, and a\"},{\"text\":\"roaring sound in your ears. There was something terrible on the other side\"},{\"text\":\"of the wall. You knew that you knew what it was, but you dared not drag it\"},{\"text\":\"into the open. It was the rats that were on the other side of the wall.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"}]","[{\"text\":\"'O'Brien!' said Winston, making an effort to control his voice. 'You know\"},{\"text\":\"this is not necessary. What is it that you want me to do?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien made no direct answer. When he spoke it was in the schoolmasterish\"}]","[{\"text\":\"sometimes affected. He looked thoughtfully into the\"},{\"text\":\"distance, as though he were addressing an audience somewhere behind\"},{\"text\":\"Winston's back.\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'By itself,' he said, 'pain is not always enough. There are occasions when\"}]","[{\"text\":\"stand out against pain, even to the point of death.\"},{\"text\":\"But for everyone there is something unendurable--something that cannot be\"},{\"text\":\"contemplated. Courage and cowardice are not involved. If you are falling\"}]","[{\"text\":\"you have come up\"},{\"text\":\"from deep water it is not cowardly to fill your lungs with air. It is\"},{\"text\":\"merely an instinct which cannot be destroyed. It is the same with the\"},{\"text\":\"rats. For you, they are unendurable. They are a form of pressure that you\"}]","[{\"text\":\"even if you wished to. You will do what is required of\"},{\"text\":\"you.'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"'But what is it, what is it? How can I do it if I don't know what it is?'\"},{\"text\":\"\"},{\"text\":\"O'Brien picked up the cage and brought it across to the nearer table.\"}]","[{\"text\":\"He set it down carefully on the baize cloth. Winston could hear the